question.text: What should I do if my deposit of RM15 has not been credited yet?
variations: Why hasn't my deposit of RM15 shown up?
What are the steps to take if my RM15 deposit is missing?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit of RM15 has not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika deposit RM15 saya belum masuk?

detailed.en: If your deposit of RM15 has not been credited yet, please wait for about 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, deposits are credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the amount is still not credited, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for further verification.
detailed.ms: Jika deposit RM15 anda belum masuk, mohon tunggu 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, deposit akan masuk dalam 1-10 minit. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum masuk, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited after uploading the receipt?
variations: Kredit xmasuk lg
Tlg tgk jp

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: If you have uploaded the receipt for the top-up and it has not been credited, please wait for 3-10 minutes for confirmation. If it still does not appear after that, please send the receipt via live chat for further assistance. If you are trying to top-up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) and it is unsuccessful, here are some steps you can try: Ensure you are using the correct method: If using Fast Payment (FPX), make sure to select TNG eWallet in the payment section and wait 1-3 minutes for the system to automatically confirm the transaction. If after 3 minutes it still does not appear, send the FPX transaction receipt to live chat for verification. If using DuitNow Transfer via TNG, ensure you select DuitNow to the bank account number, not a regular eWallet transfer. Manually upload the transaction receipt to the top-up page in the app and wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If there are still issues, try changing your internet connection (WiFi/Data), check if TNG is under maintenance, or try other methods like ATM/Transfer. If it still does not work, reply to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah memuat naik resit untuk top-up dan ia belum dikreditkan, sila tunggu dalam 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika selepas itu masih tiada, sila hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika anda cuba top-up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) dan ia tidak berjaya, berikut adalah beberapa langkah yang boleh anda cuba: Pastikan anda menggunakan kaedah yang betul: Jika menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), pastikan anda memilih TNG eWallet dalam bahagian pembayaran dan tunggu 1-3 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi secara automatik. Jika selepas 3 minit masih tiada, hantar resit transaksi FPX ke live chat untuk semakan. Jika menggunakan DuitNow Transfer melalui TNG, pastikan anda memilih DuitNow ke nombor akaun bank, bukan pemindahan eWallet biasa. Muat naik resit transaksi secara manual ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika masih ada masalah, cuba tukar rangkaian internet (WiFi/Data), semak jika TNG sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, atau cuba kaedah lain seperti ATM/Transfer. Jika masih tidak berjaya, balas kepada kami di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do when I feel like my luck is not on my side in the game?

languages.en: What should I do when I feel like my luck is not on my side in the game?
languages.ms: Apa yang patut saya lakukan apabila saya rasa nasib saya tidak menyebelahi dalam permainan?
languages.cn: 当我觉得我的运气在游戏中不在我这边时，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: In the game, there are ups and downs; sometimes luck just hasn't arrived yet. But if you stay patient, opportunities will always come! I hope in the next draw you hit big and can win a lot!
detailed.ms: Dalam permainan, ada naik turun; kadang-kadang nasib belum sampai. Tapi jika anda tetap sabar, peluang sentiasa ada! Saya harap dalam cabutan seterusnya anda dapat kemenangan besar dan boleh menang banyak!
detailed.cn: 在游戏中，有起有落；有时运气还没有到来。但如果你保持耐心，机会总会出现！我希望在下次抽奖中你能中大奖，赢得很多！

question.text: I am wondering why my top-up has not been credited yet. Can you help me check the status?
variations: Why hasn't my top-up been credited?
Can you check the status of my top-up?

languages.en: I am wondering why my top-up has not been credited yet. Can you help me check the status?
languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu mengapa top-up saya belum dikreditkan. Bolehkah anda membantu saya menyemak statusnya?

detailed.en: If the top-up has not been credited, please let me know if you used ATM/Transfer or Fast Payment (FPX). I can help check for you. If using ATM/Transfer, ensure the receipt has been uploaded to the top-up page in the app and wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If using Fast Payment (FPX), it usually gets credited within 1-3 minutes. If it has been more than 3 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification. If there are any other issues, please reply to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up belum dikreditkan, sila beritahu saya sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer atau Fast Payment (FPX). Saya boleh bantu semak untuk anda. Jika menggunakan ATM/Transfer, pastikan resit telah dimuat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), biasanya akan dikreditkan dalam 1-3 minit. Jika lebih dari 3 minit dan masih belum masuk, hantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan. Jika ada masalah lain, balas kepada kami di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Is the 918KISS platform currently undergoing maintenance, and what should I do if I encounter issues?
variations: Is 918KISS down for maintenance?
What to do if 918KISS is not working?

languages.en: Is the 918KISS platform currently undergoing maintenance, and what should I do if I encounter issues?
languages.ms: Adakah platform 918KISS sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah?

detailed.en: If the 918KISS platform is undergoing maintenance, you can try using another bank for withdrawals or wait until the maintenance is completed. If the problem persists, please contact our live chat support for further assistance. Additionally, you can try the following steps: 1. Change your internet connection (e.g., switch from Wi-Fi to mobile data or vice versa). 2. Restart your phone and try logging in again. If you still encounter errors, it is likely that 918KISS is undergoing maintenance. Please be patient, as the system will be back to normal after maintenance is completed.
detailed.ms: Jika platform 918KISS sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, anda boleh cuba menggunakan bank lain untuk pengeluaran atau tunggu sehingga penyelenggaraan selesai. Jika masalah berterusan, sila hubungi sokongan live chat kami untuk bantuan lanjut. Selain itu, anda boleh cuba langkah berikut: 1. Tukar sambungan internet (contoh: dari Wi-Fi ke data atau sebaliknya). 2. Restart telefon anda dan cuba log masuk semula. Jika anda masih menghadapi ralat, kemungkinan 918KISS sedang dalam penyelenggaraan. Mohon bersabar, kerana sistem akan kembali normal selepas penyelenggaraan selesai.

question.text: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
variations: topup
how to top up using ATM

languages.en: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun saya menggunakan ATM?
languages.cn: 我如何通过ATM充值我的账户？

detailed.en: To top up using an ATM, follow these steps: 1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers. 2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu. 3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app). 4. Enter the top-up amount (Minimum RM10). 5. Confirm the transaction and keep the receipt. 6. Take a picture of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat. 7. The top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes. Ensure the receipt is clear and complete to avoid rejection. If you have any issues or need assistance, please reply to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up menggunakan ATM, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke ATM mana-mana bank yang menyokong pemindahan antara bank. 2. Pilih menu 'Transfer' atau 'Pemindahan Wang'. 3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up dalam aplikasi). 4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10). 5. Sahkan transaksi dan simpan resit. 6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat. 7. Top-up akan diproses dalam 3-10 minit. Pastikan resit jelas dan lengkap untuk mengelakkan penolakan. Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya.
detailed.cn: 要通过ATM充值，请按照以下步骤操作：1. 前往任何支持银行间转账的银行ATM。2. 选择“转账”或“汇款”菜单。3. 输入我们的公司账户号码（请参阅应用程序中的充值页面）。4. 输入充值金额（最低RM10）。5. 确认交易并保留收据。6. 拍摄收据的照片并将其上传到应用程序中的充值页面，而不是在实时聊天中。7. 充值将在3-10分钟内处理。确保收据清晰完整，以避免拒绝。如果您有任何问题或需要帮助，请在实时聊天中回复我们。

question.text: How can I ensure that my top-up of 250 credits is processed quickly?

languages.en: How can I ensure that my top-up of 250 credits is processed quickly?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh memastikan bahawa top-up saya sebanyak 250 kredit diproses dengan cepat?

detailed.cn: 如果您的充值延迟，请确保您已在充值部分上传收据。等待3-10分钟以进行确认。如果资金仍未到账，请通过在线聊天发送收据以获得进一步帮助。希望能尽快解决！

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?

languages.cn: 我在应用程序中充值后应该做什么？

detailed.en:
Hi boss, after topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. 😊

📌 Selepas memuat naik, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi.
📌 Jika ia belum masuk selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

You can try other methods for topping up: ATM/Transfer (DuitNow / Instant Transfer) with a minimum of RM10, or Fast Payment (FPX) through other banks with a minimum of RM50. If you still encounter issues or need assistance, please contact us via live chat.

Boss boleh cuba kaedah lain untuk topup: ATM/Transfer (DuitNow / Instant Transfer) – Min RM10, atau Fast Payment (FPX) melalui bank lain – Min RM50. question.text: What should I do if my deposit hasn't been processed after sending the receipt multiple times?
variations: What happens if my deposit is delayed?
Why is my deposit taking so long?
What to do if my deposit is not successful?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit hasn't been processed after sending the receipt multiple times?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika deposit saya belum diproses selepas menghantar resit beberapa kali?

detailed.en: If your deposit hasn't been processed, you only need to upload the receipt once and wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to verify it. If you upload the same receipt twice, the system may reject the transaction and it will take longer to process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the deposit still hasn't gone through, please send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Please be patient, the system will process it as quickly as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika deposit anda belum diproses, anda hanya perlu memuat naik resit sekali sahaja dan tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkannya. Jika anda memuat naik resit yang sama dua kali, sistem mungkin akan menolak transaksi dan ia akan mengambil masa lebih lama untuk diproses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan deposit masih belum masuk, sila hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Mohon bersabar, sistem akan memprosesnya secepat mungkin!

question.text: Why am I unable to log in to the application?
variations: bos kenapa tak boleh in kis

languages.en: Why am I unable to log in to the application?
languages.ms: Bos kenapa tak boleh in kis

detailed.en:
If you are experiencing issues with logging in, you can try the following steps:

1. Close and reopen the application.
2. Log out and log back into the application, then re-enter your ID and password.
3. Try switching your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa).
4. Check if the game is under maintenance – if so, wait until it is completed.
5. If the problem persists, you can try downloading the application again using the correct link.

If you need further assistance, feel free to let me know!
detailed.ms:
Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk log masuk, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut:

1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi.
2. Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam aplikasi, kemudian salin semula ID dan kata laluan.
3. Cuba tukar sambungan internet (WiFi ke data atau sebaliknya).
4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan – jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai.
5. Jika masalah berterusan, anda boleh cuba memuat turun semula aplikasi menggunakan pautan yang betul.

Jika anda perlukan bantuan lanjut, jangan ragu untuk beritahu saya!

languages.en: Is it possible to process a payment of RM40?
languages.ms: Adakah mungkin untuk memproses pembayaran RM40?

detailed.en: If you have uploaded the receipt for a top-up of RM200, ensure it has been uploaded on the top-up page in the app. Wait for 3-10 minutes for confirmation. If the funds have not been credited yet, please send the receipt via live chat. If you have any other questions, let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah upload resit untuk top-up RM200, pastikan ia telah dimuat naik di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 3–10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika dana masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantar resit melalui live chat. Jika ada soalan lain, beritahu saya ya!
detailed.cn: 如果您已经上传了200令吉的充值收据，请确保它已在应用程序的充值页面上上传。等待3-10分钟以进行确认。如果资金仍未入账，请通过实时聊天发送收据。如果您还有其他问题，请告诉我！

question.text: What should I do if I am unable to log into 918Kiss?
variations: I can't log into 918Kiss.

detailed.en:
To resolve the login issue with 918Kiss, you can try the following steps:
1. Close and reopen the 918Kiss app.
2. Log out and log back into the Joker app, then re-enter your ID and password.
3. Try switching your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa).
4. Check if the game is under maintenance – if so, wait until it is completed.
5. If you still cannot log in, try reinstalling the game using the correct links:
   - Download 918Kiss: https://m-918kiss.com or http://b1.918kiss.com
If the problem persists, please respond to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms:
Untuk menyelesaikan masalah log masuk dengan 918Kiss, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut:
1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi 918Kiss.
2. Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam aplikasi Joker, kemudian masukkan semula ID dan kata laluan anda.
3. Cuba tukar sambungan internet (dari WiFi ke data mudah alih atau sebaliknya).
4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan – jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai.
5. Jika anda masih tidak dapat log masuk, cuba pasang semula permainan menggunakan pautan yang betul:
   - Muat Turun 918Kiss: https://m-918kiss.com atau http://b1.918kiss.com
Jika masalah berterusan, sila balas kepada kami dalam live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.
detailed.cn:
要解决918Kiss的登录问题，您可以尝试以下步骤：
1. 关闭并重新打开918Kiss应用程序。
2. 登出并重新登录Joker应用程序，然后重新输入您的ID和密码。
3. 尝试切换您的互联网连接（从WiFi切换到移动数据或反之亦然）。
4. 检查游戏是否正在维护 - 如果是，请等待完成。
5. 如果您仍然无法登录，请尝试使用正确的链接重新安装游戏：
   - 下载918Kiss: https://m-918kiss.com或http://b1.918kiss.com
如果问题仍然存在，请在实时聊天中回复我们以获取进一步的帮助。

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do if I am having trouble logging in?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah untuk log masuk?

detailed.en: Please try the following steps: 1. Change your internet connection (for example, switch from Wi-Fi to mobile data or vice versa). 2. Restart your phone and try logging in again. 3. If you still encounter an error, it is possible that 918KISS is undergoing maintenance. Please be patient, the system will be back to normal after maintenance is completed. If the issue persists, feel free to contact us again.
detailed.ms: Sila cuba langkah di bawah dulu ya: 1️⃣ Tukar sambungan internet (contoh: dari Wi-Fi ke data atau sebaliknya) 2️⃣ Restart phone dan cuba login semula 3️⃣ Kalau masih keluar error, kemungkinan 918KISS tengah maintenance. Mohon boss sabar dulu ya, sistem akan ok balik lepas maintenance selesai. Kalau masih sama juga nanti, boleh roger kami semula.

question.text: I have made a fast payment, but it hasn't been credited to my wallet. Can you help me check the status of my payment?
variations: Fast payment i xmasuk wallet
Boleh tolong check

languages.ms: Boleh tolong check

detailed.en: If you have made a fast payment, it usually takes 1-3 minutes to process. If it has been more than 3 minutes and the payment has not been credited, please check the transaction in the app first. If there is still no update, send the complete FPX transaction receipt to live chat for further verification. We will assist you as soon as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat pembayaran cepat, biasanya ia akan diproses dalam 1-3 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari 3 minit dan masih belum masuk, semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika masih tiada, hantarkan resit transaksi FPX lengkap ke live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin!

question.text: What should I do if I cannot access 918Kiss?
variations: 918kiss tak dapat masuk?
I cannot open 918Kiss.

languages.en: What should I do if I cannot access 918Kiss?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat mengakses 918Kiss?

detailed.en:
If 918Kiss cannot be opened, try the following steps:

1. Close and reopen the 918Kiss app.
2. Log out and log back into the Joker app, then re-enter your ID and Password.
3. Try switching your internet connection (from WiFi to data or vice versa).
4. Check if the game is under maintenance – if so, wait until it is completed.
5. If the problem persists, try reinstalling the game using the correct links:

Download 918Kiss:
- https://m-918kiss.com
- http://b1.918kiss.com

If the issue continues, please respond to us in the live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms:
Jika 918Kiss tidak dapat dibuka, cuba langkah-langkah berikut:

1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi 918Kiss.
2. Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam aplikasi Joker, kemudian salin semula ID dan Kata Laluan.
3. Cuba tukar sambungan internet (WiFi ke data atau sebaliknya).
4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan – jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai.
5. Jika masih ada masalah, cuba pasang semula permainan menggunakan pautan yang betul:

Muat Turun 918Kiss:
- https://m-918kiss.com
- http://b1.918kiss.com

Jika masalah berterusan, balas kepada kami dalam chat langsung untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Why hasn't my money been credited yet after topping up?
variations: Why is my top-up not showing?
When will my winnings be credited?

languages.en: Why hasn't my money been credited yet after topping up?
languages.ms: Kanapa tak masuk duit boss

detailed.en: If your top-up or winnings have not been credited, it usually takes between 3 to 10 minutes to process. If it still hasn't appeared after that, please contact support directly with your transaction details. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up atau kemenangan anda belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa antara 3 hingga 10 minit untuk diproses. Jika selepas itu masih belum muncul, sila hubungi sokongan secara langsung dengan maklumat transaksi anda. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal has not been processed yet?
variations: What steps should I take if my withdrawal is delayed?
How can I check the status of my withdrawal?

languages.en: What should I do if my withdrawal has not been processed yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pengeluaran saya belum diproses?

detailed.en:
To withdraw money from your account, follow these steps in the app:

1️⃣ Click the 'Wallet' icon (at the bottom center of the screen).
2️⃣ Select 'Withdraw'.
3️⃣ Ensure the selected bank account has a 'Primary' tag.
4️⃣ Enter the amount you wish to withdraw (Min RM10).
5️⃣ Click 'Submit' to send the withdrawal request.
6️⃣ Wait 5-30 minutes for the process to complete.

📌 Important:
✅ The name of the bank account owner must match the name registered in the app.
✅ If the bank account has not been added or you want to change it, update it first before submitting.

If there are any issues or you need assistance, just reply in the live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk mengeluarkan duit dari akaun, ikut langkah-langkah ini dalam aplikasi:

1️⃣ Klik ikon 'Wallet' (di tengah bawah skrin).
2️⃣ Pilih 'Withdraw'.
3️⃣ Pastikan akaun bank yang dipilih mempunyai tanda 'Primary'.
4️⃣ Masukkan jumlah yang ingin dikeluarkan (Min RM10).
5️⃣ Klik 'Submit' untuk menghantar permohonan pengeluaran.
6️⃣ Tunggu 5-30 minit untuk proses selesai.

📌 Penting:
✅ Nama pemilik akaun bank mesti sepadan dengan nama yang didaftarkan dalam aplikasi.
✅ Jika akaun bank belum ditambah atau ingin menukarnya, kemas kini dahulu sebelum menghantar.

Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas saja dalam live chat ya!

question.text: What should I do if I cannot log in to Kiss918?
variations: How can I resolve my login issue with Kiss918?
What steps can I take if I'm having trouble logging into Kiss918?

languages.en: What should I do if I cannot log in to Kiss918?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat log masuk ke Kiss918?
languages.cn: 如果我无法登录Kiss918，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If you cannot log in to Kiss918, try the following steps: 1. Restart your phone. 2. Switch to a different internet connection (data/WiFi). 3. If you still cannot log in, connect using a Malaysian VPN by downloading this app: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=malaysia.vpn_tap2free&hl=en&gl=US. 4. After installing, connect to a Malaysian server and try logging into Kiss918 again. If none of these methods work, it is possible that Kiss918 is undergoing maintenance, so please try logging in again later.
detailed.ms: Jika anda tidak dapat log masuk ke Kiss918, cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Mulakan semula telefon anda. 2. Tukar kepada sambungan internet yang berbeza (data/WiFi). 3. Jika anda masih tidak dapat log masuk, sambung menggunakan VPN Malaysia dengan memuat turun aplikasi ini: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=malaysia.vpn_tap2free&hl=en&gl=US. 4. Selepas memasang, sambung ke server Malaysia dan cuba log masuk ke Kiss918 semula. Jika tiada kaedah ini berfungsi, mungkin Kiss918 sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, jadi sila cuba log masuk lagi nanti.
detailed.cn: 如果您无法登录Kiss918，请尝试以下步骤：1. 重启您的手机。2. 切换到不同的互联网连接（数据/WiFi）。3. 如果您仍然无法登录，请使用马来西亚VPN连接，下载此应用程序：https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=malaysia.vpn_tap2free&hl=en&gl=US。4. 安装后，连接到马来西亚服务器，然后再次尝试登录Kiss918。如果这些方法都无效，可能Kiss918正在进行维护，请稍后再尝试登录。

question.text: What should I do if I have trouble logging in?
variations: How can I resolve login issues?
What steps can I take if I can't log in?

languages.en: What should I do if I have trouble logging in?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah log masuk?
languages.cn: 如果我登录有问题，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If you are having trouble logging in, please ensure that your username and password are correct. If you still cannot log in, try resetting your password. If the issue persists, let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda menghadapi masalah log masuk, sila pastikan nama pengguna dan kata laluan anda betul. Jika anda masih tidak dapat log masuk, cuba tetapkan semula kata laluan anda. Jika masalah berterusan, beritahu saya!
detailed.cn: 如果您登录有问题，请确保您的用户名和密码正确。如果您仍然无法登录，请尝试重置密码。如果问题仍然存在，请告诉我！

question.text: How can I upload my receipt and ensure it is processed correctly in the app?
variations: What steps do I need to follow to upload my receipt?
Is there a specific format for the receipt I need to upload?

languages.en: How can I upload my receipt and ensure it is processed correctly in the app?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh memuat naik resit saya dan memastikan ia diproses dengan betul dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: To upload your receipt, please ensure that it clearly shows the total amount, date/time, and recipient. After uploading, wait between 3-10 minutes for the system to process it. If the funds are not credited after 10 minutes, you can contact live chat for immediate assistance. If you are using Maybank, follow these steps to obtain a complete receipt: 1. Tap 'Accounts', 2. Select your bank account, 3. Tap 'View Receipts', 4. Tap the download button as shown in the image. Make sure the receipt you send is complete as per the example provided.
detailed.ms: Untuk memuat naik resit anda, sila pastikan ia menunjukkan jumlah yang jelas, tarikh/masa, dan penerima. Selepas memuat naik, tunggu antara 3-10 minit untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jika dana tidak dikredit selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Jika anda menggunakan Maybank, ikut langkah-langkah ini untuk mendapatkan resit lengkap: 1. Tekan 'Accounts', 2. Pilih akaun bank anda, 3. Tekan 'View Receipts', 4. Tekan butang muat turun seperti yang ditunjukkan dalam gambar. Pastikan resit yang anda hantar lengkap seperti contoh yang diberikan.

question.text: What should I do if the results for J3 are not showing up?
variations: keputusan J3 takda
masalahnya keputusan J3 takda
keputusan J3 tak tau mcm mana nak tau kena ke tidak

languages.en: What should I do if the results for J3 are not showing up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika keputusan J3 tidak muncul?

detailed.en: If the results for J3 are not showing up, please wait 10 minutes for the system to process. If they still do not appear, you can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see your credits. If the issue persists, I recommend contacting customer service with your transaction details for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika keputusan J3 tidak muncul, sila tunggu 10 minit untuk sistem memproses. Jika masih tiada, anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit. Jika masalah berterusan, saya sarankan untuk menghubungi khidmat pelanggan dengan butiran transaksi anda.

question.text: Why hasn't my transaction reflected yet after topping up?

languages.en: Why hasn't my transaction reflected yet after topping up?
languages.ms: Mengapa transaksi saya belum muncul selepas topup?
languages.cn: 为什么我充值后交易还没有反映？

detailed.en: If your J3 winnings have not been credited yet, please wait 10 minutes for the system to process. If it still does not appear after 10 minutes, you can contact live chat with your transaction details.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 anda belum masuk, sila tunggu 10 minit untuk sistem memproses. Jika masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda.
detailed.cn: 如果您的J3奖金尚未到账，请等待10分钟以便系统处理。如果10分钟后仍未出现，请通过实时聊天联系您交易的详细信息。

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?
languages.cn: 上传收据后我该怎么办？

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!
detailed.cn: 收据已成功上传。请稍等片刻以便系统处理。请不要再次上传相同的收据，因为这可能会减慢系统速度。感谢您的耐心和合作！

question.text: Why am I not winning anything in the game? It feels like I'm just losing money.
variations: 1 sen pun tak ada winning langsung
Sudah 600 makan duit saja
Free game susah mahu dapat

languages.en: Why am I not winning anything in the game? It feels like I'm just losing money.
languages.ms: Mengapa saya tidak menang apa-apa dalam permainan? Nampaknya saya hanya kehilangan wang.

detailed.en: It seems you are very disappointed because you haven't won anything. Sometimes luck just doesn't favor us. Don't give up, as every game has its ups and downs. If you want, you can try varying the types of games or your strategies. If there's anything else you'd like to discuss, let me know!
detailed.ms: Nampaknya anda sangat kecewa kerana tidak mendapat sebarang kemenangan. Kadang-kadang, nasib memang tidak menyebelahi kita. Jangan putus asa, kerana setiap permainan mempunyai turun naiknya. Jika anda ingin, boleh cuba variasikan jenis permainan atau strategi anda. Jika ada yang lain yang ingin dibincangkan, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: User is asking if the set they are playing is causing them to lose significantly.
variations: Memang set kasi sy kalah besar kah?

languages.en: Is the set causing me to lose significantly?
languages.ms: Memang set kasi sy kalah besar kah?

detailed.en: I understand, boss! Sometimes luck does not favor us. Don't give up, as fortune can change at any time! Keep playing patiently, and perhaps a big win will come in the next round!
detailed.ms: Faham, boss! Kadang-kadang nasib memang tidak menyebelahi kita. Jangan putus asa, kerana keberuntungan boleh berubah bila-bila masa! Teruskan bermain dengan sabar, mungkin kemenangan besar akan datang dalam pusingan seterusnya!

question.text: How can I check the status of my RM200 withdrawal?
variations: What should I do if my withdrawal hasn't been credited?
How long does it take for a withdrawal to process?

languages.en: How can I check the status of my RM200 withdrawal?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh menyemak status pengeluaran RM200 saya?
languages.cn: 我如何检查我的RM200提款状态？

detailed.en: To check the status of your withdrawal, please verify your bank account. The withdrawal process usually takes 5-30 minutes. If it has been more than 30 minutes and the funds have not been credited, please send your transaction details to live chat for immediate verification. Also, check your wallet to see if the credit has been returned. If it still hasn't been credited, send your transaction details to live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk menyemak status pengeluaran anda, sila semak akaun bank anda. Proses pengeluaran biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit. Jika sudah lebih 30 minit dan dana masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Juga, semak dalam wallet anda untuk melihat jika kredit telah dikembalikan. Jika masih belum masuk, hantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.
detailed.cn: 要检查您的提款状态，请验证您的银行账户。提款过程通常需要5-30分钟。如果超过30分钟资金仍未到账，请将您的交易详情发送到在线聊天以进行即时验证。同时检查您的钱包以查看信用是否已返回。如果仍未到账，请将您的交易详情发送到在线聊天以获取进一步帮助。

question.text: Can you help me check the status of my top-up transaction?
variations: tolong check bos
atas skali
sudah ya bos

languages.en: Can you help me check the status of my top-up transaction?
languages.ms: Tolong check status top-up saya?

detailed.en: Hi boss, once you have topped up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. After uploading, wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds are still not credited, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hi bos, kalau dah topup, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app ya. Lepas upload, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran bos!

question.text: How can I top up my account and what should I do if I have uploaded the receipt?
variations: What are the steps to top up my account?
What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: How can I top up my account and what should I do if I have uploaded the receipt?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun saya dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: To top up your account, please follow the steps provided earlier. After uploading the receipt, wait for 3-10 minutes for confirmation. If the funds are not credited after that, you can contact live chat for immediate assistance. Make sure the receipt is clear and shows the time.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up akaun anda, sila ikut langkah-langkah yang diberikan sebelum ini. Selepas memuat naik resit, tunggu dalam 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika dana masih belum dikredit selepas itu, anda boleh hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Pastikan resit jelas dan menunjukkan masa.

question.text: What are the rules regarding deposits, bonuses, and transfers between IDs in relation to betting?

languages.en: What are the rules regarding deposits, bonuses, and transfers between IDs in relation to betting?
languages.ms: Apakah peraturan mengenai deposit, bonus, dan pemindahan antara ID berkaitan dengan pertaruhan?
languages.cn: 关于存款、奖金和ID之间转账与投注的规则是什么？

detailed.en: Deposits, bonuses, and transfers between IDs can only be used for betting purposes. Full withdrawals can only be made after winning more than 30% of the deposit.
detailed.ms: Deposit, bonus, dan pemindahan antara ID hanya boleh digunakan untuk tujuan pertaruhan. Pengeluaran penuh hanya boleh dilakukan setelah menang lebih daripada 30% deposit.
detailed.cn: 存款、奖金和ID之间的转账只能用于投注目的。只有在赢得超过30%的存款后才能进行全额提款。

question.text: What should I do if my account has been suspended due to multiple top-ups with a different bank name?

languages.en: What should I do if my account has been suspended due to multiple top-ups with a different bank name?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika akaun saya telah disekat kerana beberapa top-up dengan nama bank yang berbeza?
languages.cn: 如果我的账户因多次使用不同银行名称充值而被暂停，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: Your account has been suspended because you have made three top-ups using a bank name that does not match the registered name. We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause and thank you for your understanding.
detailed.ms: Akaun anda telah disekat kerana anda telah membuat tiga top-up menggunakan nama bank yang tidak sepadan dengan nama yang didaftarkan. Kami memohon maaf atas segala kesulitan dan terima kasih atas pemahaman anda.
detailed.cn: 您的账户已被暂停，因为您使用与注册名称不匹配的银行名称进行了三次充值。我们对造成的任何不便表示歉意，并感谢您的理解。

question.text: What should I do if I entered the wrong amount during the top-up process?
variations: Jumlah salah bosw
Dua Dua reject bosw

languages.en: What should I do if I entered the wrong amount during the top-up process?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya memasukkan amaun yang salah semasa proses top-up?

detailed.en: If you have entered the wrong amount during the top-up, don't worry! Wait for the system to reject the transaction first, then re-upload with the correct amount on the top-up page in the app. If there are still issues or you want to check the status, reply to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memasukkan amaun yang salah semasa top-up, jangan risau! Tunggu sistem untuk menolak transaksi itu terlebih dahulu, kemudian muat naik semula dengan amaun yang betul di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. Jika masih ada masalah atau anda ingin menyemak status, balas kepada kami di live chat ya.

question.text: I am having trouble logging in to my account. What should I do?
variations: X msok lgi ke

languages.en: I am having trouble logging in to my account. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya mengalami masalah untuk log masuk ke akaun saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
languages.cn: 我在登录我的账户时遇到问题。我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If you are experiencing issues logging in, you can try the following steps: 1. Double-check your username and password. 2. Ensure your internet connection is stable. 3. Try resetting your password if necessary. If the problem persists, please contact customer support for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk log masuk, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Semak semula nama pengguna dan kata laluan anda. 2. Pastikan sambungan internet anda stabil. 3. Cuba untuk menetapkan semula kata laluan jika perlu. Jika masalah masih berterusan, sila hubungi sokongan pelanggan untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!
detailed.cn: 如果您在登录时遇到问题，可以尝试以下步骤：1. 再次检查您的用户名和密码。2. 确保您的互联网连接稳定。3. 如果需要，请尝试重置密码。如果问题仍然存在，请联系客户支持以获得进一步的帮助。祝好运！

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?
languages.cn: 上传收据后我该怎么办？

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!
detailed.cn: 收据已成功上传。请稍等片刻以便系统处理。请不要再次上传相同的收据，因为这可能会减慢系统速度。感谢您的耐心和合作！

question.text: What does '2N' mean in the context of betting?
variations: What is the meaning of '2N' in betting?
Can you explain '2N' in betting terms?

languages.en: What does '2N' mean in the context of betting?
languages.ms: Apa maksud '2N' dalam konteks pertaruhan?

detailed.en: '2N' refers to a betting category that includes all prizes for the last two digits of a 4D number. For example, if the winning 4D number is 1234, then '2N' will consider the last two digits, which are 34. This means all combinations ending with 34 will win.
detailed.ms: '2N' merujuk kepada kategori pertaruhan yang meliputi semua hadiah untuk dua digit terakhir dari nombor 4D. Jadi, jika nombor 4D yang menang adalah 1234, maka 2N akan mengambil kira dua digit terakhir, iaitu 34. Ini bermakna semua kombinasi yang berakhir dengan 34 akan menang.

question.text: What should I do if I cannot log into Kiss918?
variations: I can't log in to Kiss918.

languages.en: What should I do if I cannot log into Kiss918?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat log masuk ke Kiss918?

detailed.en: If you cannot log into Kiss918, try the following steps: 1️⃣ Restart your phone. 2️⃣ Change your internet connection to another line (data/WiFi). 3️⃣ If you still cannot log in, connect using a Malaysian VPN – download this app: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=malaysia.vpn_tap2free&hl=en&gl=US. 4️⃣ After installing, connect to a Malaysian server, then try logging into Kiss918 again. detailed.en: If your withdrawal has not been approved yet, don't worry! It usually takes between 5 to 30 minutes to process. We will assist you with the verification.

question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk menukar ID dalam aplikasi Joker?
variations: MCM mana mau tukar id?
kasi tukar

languages.ms: Bagaimana cara untuk menukar ID dalam aplikasi Joker?

detailed.ms:
Untuk tukar ID, anda perlu ikut langkah-langkah berikut:

1️⃣ Buka aplikasi Joker dan log masuk.
2️⃣ Pergi ke bahagian "More Game" di sudut kanan bawah.
3️⃣ Pilih ikon mesin slot 🎰 untuk masuk ke menu permainan slot.
4️⃣ Pilih Mega888 dan salin ID serta kata laluan yang dipaparkan.
5️⃣ Pergi ke "Wallet" dalam aplikasi Joker.
6️⃣ Pilih "Transfer" > Pilih Mega888 > Masukkan jumlah yang ingin dipindahkan.
7️⃣ Klik "Confirm" dan kredit akan dipindahkan ke Mega888.

Jika ada masalah semasa proses pemindahan, jangan ragu untuk hubungi sokongan live chat ya, boss! 😊

variations: What to do if my 4D winnings haven't been credited?
How long does it take for 4D winnings to appear in my wallet?

languages.en: I have won a 4D number, but the money has not yet been credited to my account. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah menang nombor 4D, tetapi wang belum lagi dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have won a 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little longer today. The winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please check the app from time to time.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah menang nombor 4D, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses dan mungkin mengambil sedikit masa hari ini. Duit kemenangan akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam wallet anda. Sila semak aplikasi dari semasa ke semasa.

question.text: What should I do if I have more questions or need assistance?

languages.en: What should I do if I have more questions or need assistance?
languages.ms: Apa yang harus saya lakukan jika saya mempunyai lebih banyak soalan atau memerlukan bantuan?
languages.cn: 如果我还有更多问题或需要帮助，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If you have any further questions, feel free to ask! I hope today is filled with great luck and prosperity!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mempunyai sebarang soalan lagi, jangan ragu untuk bertanya! Semoga hari ini penuh dengan nasib baik dan kemakmuran!
detailed.cn: 如果您还有其他问题，请随时询问！希望今天充满好运和繁荣！

question.text: What assistance can I provide you with today, boss?
variations: Bos
Hi boss, ada apa yang saya boleh bantu?

languages.en: What assistance can I provide you with today, boss?
languages.ms: Apa bantuan yang boleh saya berikan kepada anda hari ini, bos?
languages.cn: 今天我能为您提供什么帮助，老板？

detailed.en: I hope you have a lot of ONG and a big jackpot today! If there's anything else, feel free to reply!
detailed.ms: Saya harap anda dapat banyak ONG dan jackpot besar hari ini! Jika ada apa-apa lagi, jangan ragu untuk balas ya!
detailed.cn: 我希望你今天能获得很多ONG和大奖！如果还有其他问题，请随时回复！

question.text: What should I do after topping up to ensure my transaction is processed correctly?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up to ensure my transaction is processed correctly?

detailed.en: Hi boss, after topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. 😊 After uploading, wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it hasn't been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!

question.text: How can I withdraw money from my account and what should I do if the withdrawal hasn't been processed yet?
variations: saya withdraw duit
tak masuk lagi

languages.en: How can I withdraw money from my account and what should I do if the withdrawal hasn't been processed yet?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh mengeluarkan duit dari akaun saya dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pengeluaran belum diproses?

detailed.en: To withdraw money from your account, follow these steps in the app: 1. Click the 'Wallet' icon (at the bottom center of the screen). 2. Select 'Withdraw'. 3. Ensure the selected bank has a 'Primary' tag. 4. Enter the amount you wish to withdraw (Min RM10). 5. Click 'Submit' to send the withdrawal request. 6. Wait 5-30 minutes for the process to complete. If the withdrawal has not been processed after 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of the withdrawal receipt to us for investigation. If it has been more than 30 minutes, check your bank account and if it still hasn't arrived, send the transaction details to live chat for immediate review.
detailed.ms: Untuk mengeluarkan duit dari akaun anda, ikut langkah-langkah ini dalam aplikasi: 1. Klik ikon 'Wallet' (di tengah bawah skrin). 2. Pilih 'Withdraw'. 3. Pastikan bank yang dipilih mempunyai tanda 'Primary'. 4. Masukkan jumlah yang ingin dikeluarkan (Min RM10). 5. Klik 'Submit' untuk menghantar permohonan pengeluaran. 6. Tunggu 5-30 minit untuk proses selesai. Jika pengeluaran duit sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum masuk, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit pengeluaran kepada kami. Jika sudah lebih 30 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: Can you confirm if the receipt has been successfully uploaded and if I need to wait for the system to process it?

languages.en: Can you confirm if the receipt has been successfully uploaded and if I need to wait for the system to process it?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda mengesahkan jika resit telah berjaya dimuat naik dan jika saya perlu menunggu sistem memprosesnya?
languages.cn: 您能确认收据是否已成功上传，以及我是否需要等待系统处理吗？

detailed.en: Hi boss, the receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. 🙏 Please do not upload the same receipt again, as it will slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation! 😊🔥
detailed.ms: Hai bos, resit sudah berjaya diupload ya. Mohon bos tunggu sebentar untuk sistem proses. 🙏 Jangan upload resit yang sama lagi ya, nanti sistem akan jadi lambat. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama bos! 😊🔥
detailed.cn: 嗨，老板，收据已成功上传。请稍等片刻，让系统处理。🙏 请不要再次上传相同的收据，否则系统会变慢。感谢您的耐心和合作！😊🔥

question.text: Why hasn't my deposit been credited yet?
variations: boss deposit belum masuk

languages.en: Why hasn't my deposit been credited yet?
languages.ms: boss deposit belum masuk

detailed.en: Hi bossku ~ Please make the transfer using the bank account provided in your app. Check the bank account in your app before topping up. Thank you! ❌ Do not save the bank account as a favorite. ❌
detailed.ms: Hi bossku ~ Sila banking ikut bank acc yg disediakan dlm APPS anda ya. sila semak bank acc dlm APPS anda sebelum nak topup ya , tq bossku ❤ ❌Jgn save bank account favourite ye❌

question.text: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited to my account yet?
variations: What to do if top-up is not showing?
How long does it take for a top-up to appear in my account?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited to my account yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?
languages.cn: 如果我的充值尚未到账，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If your top-up hasn't been credited, you only need to upload the receipt once and wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If you upload the same receipt twice, the system may reject the transaction and it will take longer to process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it still hasn't appeared, send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Please be patient, the system will process it as quickly as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum dikreditkan, anda hanya perlu memuat naik resit sekali sahaja dan tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika anda memuat naik resit yang sama dua kali, sistem mungkin akan menolak transaksi dan ia akan mengambil masa lebih lama untuk diproses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan ia masih belum muncul, hantarkan resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Mohon bersabar, sistem akan memprosesnya secepat mungkin!
detailed.cn: 如果您的充值尚未到账，您只需上传收据一次，并等待1-10分钟以便系统确认。如果您上传相同的收据两次，系统可能会拒绝交易，处理时间会更长。如果超过10分钟仍未到账，请将交易收据发送到在线聊天以进行即时验证。请耐心等待，系统会尽快处理！

question.text: Saya sudah topup Maybank tetapi nombor akaun sudah ditukar, apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
variations: Saya sudah topup tetapi nombor akaun sudah ditukar.
Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika nombor akaun saya sudah ditukar setelah topup?

languages.en: I have topped up Maybank but my account number has changed, what should I do?
languages.ms: Saya sudah topup Maybank tetapi nombor akaun sudah ditukar, apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have topped up through Maybank but your account number has changed, there may be an issue with the transaction. Please check your transaction details and ensure that you have entered the correct information. If there are discrepancies, you need to report this issue immediately through live chat with the complete transaction receipt. If you accidentally transferred funds to the wrong account, those funds may not be recoverable. If there's anything else I can assist you with, just let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah top-up melalui Maybank tetapi nombor akaun sudah ditukar, mungkin ada masalah dengan transaksi tersebut. Sila semak butiran transaksi anda dan pastikan bahawa anda telah memasukkan maklumat yang betul. Jika ada ketidaksesuaian, anda perlu melaporkan isu ini segera melalui live chat dengan resit transaksi yang lengkap. Jika anda secara tidak sengaja memindahkan dana ke akaun yang salah, dana tersebut mungkin tidak dapat dipulihkan.

question.text: What should I do to send the receipt for the last claim to the Top-Up section?

languages.en: What should I do to send the receipt for the last claim to the Top-Up section?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan untuk menghantar resit bagi tuntutan terakhir ke bahagian Top-Up?

detailed.en: Please resend the receipt to the Top-Up section as this is the final claim. Make sure to check the list of bank accounts in the app before making the transfer to avoid any mistakes. Thank you for your cooperation!
detailed.ms: Sila hantar semula resit kepada bahagian Top-Up kerana ini adalah tuntutan terakhir. Mohon semak senarai akaun bank dalam aplikasi sebelum membuat pemindahan untuk mengelakkan sebarang kesilapan. Terima kasih atas kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do if I have uploaded my bank slip multiple times and haven't received confirmation yet?
variations: What if I uploaded the receipt twice?
What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do if I have uploaded my bank slip multiple times and haven't received confirmation yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah memuat naik slip bank saya beberapa kali dan belum menerima pengesahan?

detailed.en: If you have uploaded the receipt twice for the top-up, there is no need to worry. The system only requires one receipt for verification. Sending the same receipt multiple times may lead to rejection. Please wait 3-10 minutes for processing. If there are any issues, feel free to contact us via live chat. We are here to help!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memuat naik resit dua kali untuk top-up, tidak perlu risau. Sistem hanya memerlukan satu resit untuk pemeriksaan. Menghantar resit yang sama berulang kali mungkin menyebabkan penolakan. Sila tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pemprosesan. Jika ada sebarang isu, jangan ragu untuk hubungi kami melalui live chat. Kami sedia membantu!

question.text: I made a mistake with my transaction and need help to resolve it. What should I do if my top-up amount is incorrect?
variations: What should I do if I entered the wrong amount for my top-up?
How can I fix a mistake in my transaction?

languages.en: I made a mistake with my transaction and need help to resolve it. What should I do if my top-up amount is incorrect?
languages.ms: Saya telah membuat kesilapan dengan transaksi saya dan memerlukan bantuan untuk menyelesaikannya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika amaun top-up saya salah?

detailed.en: If you have entered the wrong amount in your top-up, please resend the transaction by uploading the correct receipt with the accurate amount. The system will process your updated top-up within 3-10 minutes. If the credit still does not appear, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your receipt for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memasukkan amaun yang salah dalam top-up, sila hantar semula transaksi dengan memuat naik resit yang betul dengan amaun yang tepat. Sistem akan memproses top-up anda yang dikemas kini dalam masa 3-10 minit. Jika kredit masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin resit anda untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: How can I confirm my transfer of RM70 to the Maybank account of Kabali Enterprise?
variations: mcm mana ya...?
saya sudah transfer rm70 ke acc maybank kabali enterpise.

languages.ms: saya sudah transfer rm70 ke acc maybank kabali enterpise.

detailed.en: To complete the top-up via bank transfer, please follow these steps: 1. Close the red notification by pressing the (x) button. 2. Select the bank you used for the transfer (e.g., Maybank). 3. Enter the amount transferred and upload a clear receipt on the top-up page. 4. After submitting, wait 1-10 minutes for the system to process your transaction. If the credit still does not appear after 10 minutes, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your receipt for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Untuk melengkapkan top-up melalui pemindahan bank, sila ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Tutup notifikasi merah dengan menekan butang (x). 2. Pilih bank yang anda gunakan untuk pemindahan (contohnya, Maybank). 3. Masukkan jumlah yang telah dipindahkan dan muat naik resit yang jelas di halaman top-up. 4. Setelah menghantar, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem memproses transaksi anda. Jika kredit masih tidak muncul selepas 10 minit, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin resit anda untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya, boss! 😊

question.text: What should I do if I am experiencing issues with logging into the game or if the game is not loading properly?
variations: Game not loading
Login issues with the game

languages.en: What should I do if I am experiencing issues with logging into the game or if the game is not loading properly?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya mengalami masalah untuk log masuk ke permainan atau jika permainan tidak dimuatkan dengan betul?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing issues with logging into the game or if the game is not loading properly, try the following steps: Close and reopen the game app. Log out and log back into the Joker App, then re-enter your ID and Password. Change your internet connection (try WiFi or mobile data). Check if the game is under maintenance – if it is, wait until it is completed. If you still cannot access the game, consider using a VPN. You can download a VPN from the link provided, install it, and connect to Malaysia before trying to log in again. If problems persist, send a screenshot to live chat for immediate assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk log masuk ke permainan atau jika permainan tidak dimuatkan dengan betul, cuba langkah-langkah berikut: Tutup & buka semula aplikasi permainan. Logout & login semula ke Joker App, kemudian masukkan semula ID & Kata Laluan anda. Tukar sambungan internet (cuba WiFi atau data mudah alih). Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan – jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai. Jika anda masih tidak dapat mengakses permainan, pertimbangkan untuk menggunakan VPN. Anda boleh memuat turun VPN dari pautan yang diberikan, pasang dan sambungkan ke Malaysia sebelum mencuba log masuk semula. Jika masalah berterusan, hantarkan tangkapan skrin ke sembang langsung untuk bantuan segera.

question.text: How do I change my bank account in the application?
variations: tukar bank ke

languages.en: How do I change my bank account in the application?
languages.ms: tukar bank ke

detailed.en: To change your bank account in the application, go to the 'Wallet' section, select 'Withdraw', and then choose 'Add Account' to enter your new bank details. Ensure that the account name matches the registered profile. If you encounter any issues, please contact our live chat support for assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk menukar akaun bank dalam aplikasi, sila pergi ke bahagian 'Wallet', pilih 'Withdraw', dan kemudian pilih 'Add Account' untuk memasukkan butiran bank baru anda. Pastikan nama akaun sepadan dengan profil yang didaftarkan. Jika ada sebarang masalah, sila hubungi sokongan live chat kami.

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been approved after a top-up?
variations: credit saya x aprove
top-up belum dikreditkan

languages.en: What should I do if my credit has not been approved after a top-up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kredit saya tidak diluluskan selepas top-up?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited, make sure you have uploaded the transaction receipt in the top-up section of the app. Wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to process. If it is still not credited after 10 minutes, please send the transaction receipt via live chat for immediate assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum dikreditkan, pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit transaksi di bahagian top-up dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantar resit transaksi melalui live chat untuk bantuan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: I won in the 4D lottery yesterday, but I haven't received the winnings from the Magic Box feature. What should I do?
variations: What happens if I win but don't receive my Magic Box winnings?
How can I check my Magic Box winnings after winning 4D?

languages.en: I won in the 4D lottery yesterday, but I haven't received the winnings from the Magic Box feature. What should I do?
languages.ms: Semalam I ada menang 4d tapi duit yang magic box tak dapat?

detailed.en: If you win in the Magic Box, your winnings and additional bonuses should be credited automatically based on the payout rate. However, if the credit does not appear, please take a screenshot of the results from the Joker app and send it to us for verification. Also, check your ticket details for specific letter codes (like G or H) that indicate your win. If you need further assistance, please contact live chat support for immediate help. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Oh, saya faham, boss! Jika anda menang dalam Magic Box, sepatutnya kemenangan dan bonus tambahan akan dikreditkan secara automatik berdasarkan kadar pembayaran. Namun, jika kredit tidak muncul, sila ambil tangkapan skrin keputusan dari aplikasi Joker dan hantarkan kepada kami untuk pengesahan. Juga, semak butiran tiket anda untuk kod huruf tertentu (seperti G atau H) yang menunjukkan kemenangan anda. Jika anda memerlukan bantuan lanjut, sila hubungi sokongan live chat untuk bantuan segera. Semoga berjaya, boss! 😊

question.text: How can I ensure my top-up at Kabali Smart is processed correctly and what steps should I follow?
variations: What should I do if my top-up isn't credited?
How do I upload my receipt for the top-up?

languages.en: How can I ensure my top-up at Kabali Smart is processed correctly and what steps should I follow?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh memastikan top-up saya di Kabali Smart diproses dengan betul dan langkah-langkah apa yang harus saya ikuti?

detailed.en: To top-up at Kabali Smart, follow these steps: 1. Use Instant Transfer / DuitNow (do not use IBG). 2. Enter the correct company account number and amount. 3. Write your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' if using online banking. 4. Upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app (not in live chat). 5. The top-up process will take 3-10 minutes. If you have uploaded the receipt and the funds are still not credited after waiting, please send the receipt via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk top-up di Kabali Smart, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Gunakan Instant Transfer / DuitNow (jangan gunakan IBG). 2. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat dan jumlah yang betul. 3. Tulis JOKER ID anda dalam 'Recipient Reference' jika menggunakan perbankan dalam talian. 4. Muat naik resit ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi (bukan dalam live chat). 5. Proses top-up akan mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika anda telah muat naik resit dan dana masih belum dikreditkan selepas itu, sila hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Saya hendak update nombor telefon, tetapi TAC tidak sampai ke nombor baru 0133488938. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
variations: TAC tidak masuk ke nombor baru 0133488938
Kenapa saya tidak menerima TAC untuk nombor baru saya?

languages.en: I want to update my phone number, but the TAC is not reaching the new number 0133488938. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya hendak update nombor telefon, tetapi TAC tidak sampai ke nombor baru 0133488938. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you are not receiving the TAC for the new number 0133488938, there may be several reasons. Ensure that the number you entered is correct and active. If you still do not receive the TAC, you can try to resend the TAC request. If the problem persists, it is best to contact customer service for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda tidak menerima TAC untuk nombor baru 0133488938, mungkin ada beberapa sebab. Pastikan nombor yang anda masukkan adalah betul dan aktif. Jika masih tidak menerima TAC, anda boleh cuba untuk menghantar semula permintaan TAC. Jika masalah berterusan, lebih baik hubungi khidmat pelanggan untuk mendapatkan bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What are the details of the recent Toto lottery win?
variations: Can you provide information about the Toto lottery results?
What was the winning number for the Toto lottery?

languages.en: What are the details of the recent Toto lottery win?

detailed.en: Congratulations! The recent Toto lottery win was for the number 5787, and the winner received RM6,500.00.

en: What are the next steps for claiming the prize?
How often does the Toto lottery occur?

question.text: What should I do with my old bank account that I no longer use for transactions?

languages.en: What should I do with my old bank account that I no longer use for transactions?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan dengan akaun bank lama saya yang tidak lagi saya gunakan untuk transaksi?
languages.cn: 我应该如何处理我不再使用的旧银行账户？

detailed.en: Please follow the bank account listed in your Joker app for transfers. This is the last claim. Any future deposits into this old account will be considered void. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Sila ikut akaun bank yang tertera dalam aplikasi Joker anda untuk pemindahan. Ini adalah tuntutan terakhir. Sebarang deposit masa depan ke dalam akaun lama ini akan dianggap tidak sah. Terima kasih!
detailed.cn: 请按照您Joker应用程序中列出的银行账户进行转账。这是最后一次索赔。未来存入此旧账户的任何款项将被视为无效。谢谢！

question.text: What should I do if I want to transfer money for top-up using the bank account in the app?

languages.en: What should I do if I want to transfer money for top-up using the bank account in the app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya ingin memindahkan wang untuk top-up menggunakan akaun bank dalam aplikasi?
languages.cn: 如果我想使用应用程序中的银行账户进行充值，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: Please follow the bank account list in the app for your transfer. Ensure you use the account displayed on the top-up page to ensure a smooth transaction. Do not 'Favorite' our bank account as the account number may change from time to time. If you have any other questions, feel free to contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Sila ikut senarai bank dalam aplikasi untuk pemindahan anda. Pastikan anda menggunakan akaun yang dipaparkan di halaman top-up untuk memastikan transaksi berjalan lancar. Jangan 'Favorit' akaun bank kami kerana nombor akaun mungkin berubah dari semasa ke semasa. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang pertanyaan lain, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat.
detailed.cn: 请按照应用程序中的银行账户列表进行转账。确保使用充值页面上显示的账户，以确保交易顺利进行。请不要将我们的银行账户设为“收藏”，因为账户号码可能会不时更改。如果您有其他问题，请随时通过在线聊天与我们联系。

question.text: Di mana saya boleh berkongsi kredit dan bagaimana jika saya berkongsi dengan ID yang salah?
variations: Bagaimana cara berkongsi kredit?
Apa yang perlu dilakukan jika saya berkongsi kredit dengan ID yang salah?

languages.ms: Di mana saya boleh berkongsi kredit dan bagaimana jika saya berkongsi dengan ID yang salah?

detailed.ms:
Jika anda telah berkongsi kredit dengan ID yang salah, maaf ya, sistem tidak dapat mengembalikan secara automatik.

📌 Apa yang boleh dilakukan:
1️⃣ Sila berikan JOKER ID yang anda kongsi secara salah dan jumlah kredit yang terlibat.
2️⃣ Kami akan cuba menghubungi pemilik ID tersebut dan meminta mereka untuk mengembalikan kredit dengan cara yang sama (Credit Share).
3️⃣ Namun, tiada jaminan bahawa kredit dapat dikembalikan, ia bergantung kepada pemilik ID yang menerimanya.

📌 Lain kali, pastikan ID yang dimasukkan adalah betul sebelum menekan butang hantar ya!

Jika ada soalan lain, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya, boss! 😊

question.text: What should I do if my top-up is delayed after I have made a bank transfer?
variations: What to do if my top-up is slow?
How long does it take for a top-up to reflect after a bank transfer?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up is delayed after I have made a bank transfer?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya lambat selepas saya membuat pemindahan bank?

detailed.en: If your top-up is delayed, please let me know if you are using ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). For ATM/Transfer, please upload your receipt in the top-up section and wait 1-10 minutes; for FPX, the funds should appear within 1-10 minutes. If the delay is longer, please send a full screenshot via live chat for further review.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda lambat, sila beritahu saya sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX). Untuk ATM/Transfer, sila muat naik resit anda di bahagian top-up dan tunggu 1-10 minit; untuk FPX, dana sepatutnya muncul dalam 1-10 minit. Jika kelewatan lebih lama, sila hantar tangkapan skrin penuh melalui live chat untuk semakan.

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal hasn't been credited to my bank account after 30 minutes?

detailed.en: If your withdrawal has not been credited after 30 minutes, you should check your bank account. The withdrawal process usually takes 5-30 minutes. If it has been more than 30 minutes and the funds are still not credited, please send your transaction details to live chat for immediate verification. Also, check your wallet to see if the credit has been returned. If it is still not credited, send your transaction details to live chat for immediate assistance.

Jika sudah lebih 30 minit dan dana masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantar butiran transaksi anda ke live chat untuk pengesahan segera. Juga, semak dalam wallet anda untuk melihat jika kredit telah dikembalikan. Jika masih belum dikreditkan, hantar butiran transaksi anda ke live chat untuk bantuan segera.

question.text: How can I make a fast payment for my top-up using Touch 'n Go?
variations: Nk bt mnm mna bos

languages.en: How can I make a fast payment for my top-up using Touch 'n Go?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh membuat pembayaran cepat untuk tambah nilai saya menggunakan Touch 'n Go?
languages.cn: 我如何使用Touch 'n Go进行快速支付以充值？

detailed.en: To top up using Touch 'n Go Fast Payment (FPX), follow these steps: 1. Go to the top-up page in the app. 2. Select 'Fast Payment (FPX)'. 3. Choose Touch 'n Go as the payment method. 4. Enter the top-up amount (Min RM50). 5. Confirm the transaction and complete the payment in the TNG app. 6. Wait 1-10 minutes for the system to automatically verify the transaction. If it takes more than 10 minutes, send the transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Untuk topup menggunakan Touch 'n Go Fast Payment (FPX), ikut langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke halaman topup dalam app. 2. Pilih 'Fast Payment (FPX)'. 3. Pilih Touch 'n Go sebagai kaedah pembayaran. 4. Masukkan jumlah topup (Min RM50). 5. Sahkan transaksi & lengkapkan pembayaran dalam app TNG. 6. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi secara automatik. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan.
detailed.cn: 要使用Touch 'n Go快速支付(FPX)进行充值，请按照以下步骤操作：1. 在应用程序中转到充值页面。2. 选择“快速支付(FPX)”。3. 选择Touch 'n Go作为支付方式。4. 输入充值金额（最低RM50）。5. 确认交易并在TNG应用程序中完成支付。6. 等待1-10分钟以便系统自动验证交易。如果超过10分钟仍未到账，请将交易收据发送到在线聊天进行验证。

question.text: Why am I unable to top up my account and upload the receipt?
variations: kenapa tak bole topup
xbole upload resit

languages.en: Why am I unable to top up my account and upload the receipt?
languages.ms: Kenapa tak bole topup dan upload resit?

detailed.en: If your top-up hasn't gone through, there could be several reasons. Please wait between 3-10 minutes after uploading the receipt for the system to process your top-up. If there is still no update after that, please contact live chat support with your complete receipt. The minimum amount for top-up is RM10. If you tried to top up RM5, that is insufficient. You need to add another RM5 and send both receipts to live chat for processing. If you are unable to upload the receipt, you can try the following steps: 1. Restart your phone or close and reopen the app. 2. Change your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa). 3. Ensure your internet connection is stable before trying again. If the problem persists, you can send the receipt directly to live chat support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, mungkin ada beberapa sebab. Sila tunggu antara 3-10 minit selepas anda memuat naik resit untuk sistem memproses top-up anda. Jika selepas itu masih tiada, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan resit lengkap anda. Jumlah minimum untuk top-up adalah RM10. Jika anda cuba top-up RM5, itu tidak mencukupi. Anda perlu tambah lagi RM5 dan hantar kedua-dua resit ke live chat untuk kami proses. Jika anda tidak dapat memuat naik resit, mungkin ada beberapa langkah yang boleh dicuba: 1. Mulakan semula telefon atau tutup dan buka semula aplikasi. 2. Tukar rangkaian internet (daripada WiFi ke data mudah alih atau sebaliknya). 3. Pastikan sambungan internet anda stabil sebelum mencuba lagi. Jika masalah masih berterusan, anda boleh menghantar resit secara langsung ke sokongan live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut.

question.text: Can you provide details about 2D betting in the 4D lottery system?
variations: What is 2D betting?
How does 2D betting work?
Can you explain 2D betting rules?

languages.en: Can you provide details about 2D betting in the 4D lottery system?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda memberikan butiran tentang pertaruhan 2D dalam sistem loteri 4D?

detailed.en: For 2D betting, you need to select two digits from the 4D number you purchased. A win for 2D will only occur if the numbers you choose match the last two digits of the winning number. Additionally, 2a, 2b, 2c, 2d, 2e, and 2n refer to different types of bets within the 4D system. 2a is a fixed two-digit bet, 2b is a variable two-digit bet, 2c is a two-digit bet with specific combinations, 2d is a two-digit bet with certain conditions, 2e is a two-digit bet with additional options, and 2n is an unlimited two-digit bet.
detailed.ms: Untuk pertaruhan 2D, anda perlu memilih dua digit dari nombor 4D yang anda beli. Kemenangan untuk 2D hanya akan berlaku jika nombor yang anda pilih sepadan dengan dua digit terakhir dari nombor yang menang. Selain itu, 2a, 2b, 2c, 2d, 2e, dan 2n merujuk kepada jenis pertaruhan yang berbeza dalam sistem 4D. 2a adalah pertaruhan dua digit tetap, 2b adalah pertaruhan dua digit boleh berubah, 2c adalah pertaruhan dua digit dengan kombinasi tertentu, 2d adalah pertaruhan dua digit dengan syarat tertentu, 2e adalah pertaruhan dua digit dengan pilihan tambahan, dan 2n adalah pertaruhan dua digit yang tidak terhad.

detailed.en: To top up using DuitNow, follow these steps: 1. Open your banking app and select DuitNow Transfer. 2. Enter the company account number and the correct amount (Min RM10 for ATM/Transfer, Min RM50 for Fast Payment). 3. Confirm the transaction and take a screenshot of the complete receipt. 4. Upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat. 5. Wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If your account is frozen, it is usually due to suspicious activity or transaction errors. I recommend contacting our customer service via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk tambah nilai menggunakan DuitNow, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka aplikasi perbankan anda dan pilih Transfer DuitNow. 2. Muat naik resit ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat. 5. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika akaun anda dibekukan, biasanya disebabkan oleh aktiviti yang mencurigakan atau kesilapan dalam transaksi. Saya sarankan anda hubungi khidmat pelanggan kami melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.
