detailed.en: After you upload the top-up receipt, the system requires about 3-10 minutes to process it. If you submit the same receipt multiple times, it may cause the system to reject that receipt. Therefore, it is better to send only one receipt. If you have any other issues, feel free to contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Selepas anda memuat naik resit top-up, sistem memerlukan masa sekitar 3-10 minit untuk memprosesnya. Jika anda menghantar resit yang sama berkali-kali, ia boleh menyebabkan sistem menolak resit tersebut. Jadi, lebih baik hantar satu resit sahaja. Jika anda mempunyai masalah lain, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami melalui live chat.
detailed.cn: 在您上传充值收据后，系统需要大约3-10分钟来处理。如果您多次提交相同的收据，可能会导致系统拒绝该收据。因此，最好只发送一张收据。如果您有其他问题，请随时通过在线聊天与我们联系。

question.text: How can I transfer RM50 to top up my account?
variations: bos in rm50 ternspor duit ya

languages.en: How can I transfer RM50 to top up my account?
languages.ms: bos in rm50 ternspor duit ya

detailed.en:
To top up your account, follow these steps: 

🔹 ATM/Transfer (Min RM10) 
1️⃣ Use Instant Transfer or DuitNow (❌ Do not use IBG). 
2️⃣ Enter the company's account number and the correct amount. 
3️⃣ Write your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' (if using online banking). 
4️⃣ Upload the receipt on the top-up page in the app. 
5️⃣ Wait 3-10 minutes for processing. 

🔹 Fast Payment (FPX) (Min RM50, faster) 
1️⃣ Go to the top-up page in the app. 
2️⃣ Select Fast Payment (FPX) and your preferred bank. 
3️⃣ Enter the amount and confirm the transaction. 
4️⃣ Wait 1-3 minutes for automatic confirmation. 

📌 Ensure the bank account name matches the name in the app. If there are any issues, reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top up akaun anda, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 

🔹 ATM/Transfer (Min RM10) 
1️⃣ Gunakan Instant Transfer atau DuitNow (❌ Jangan gunakan IBG). 
2️⃣ Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat dan jumlah yang betul. 
3️⃣ Tulis JOKER ID anda dalam 'Recipient Reference' (jika menggunakan perbankan dalam talian). 
4️⃣ Muat naik resit di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. 
5️⃣ Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk proses. 

🔹 Fast Payment (FPX) (Min RM50, lebih cepat) 
1️⃣ Pergi ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. 
2️⃣ Pilih Fast Payment (FPX) dan bank pilihan anda. 
3️⃣ Masukkan jumlah dan sahkan transaksi. 
4️⃣ Tunggu 1-3 minit untuk pengesahan automatik. 

📌 Pastikan nama akaun bank sepadan dengan nama dalam aplikasi. Jika ada masalah, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya!

question.text: What should I do if the deposit name is different from the registered name for a refund?

languages.en: What should I do if the deposit name is different from the registered name for a refund?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika nama deposit berbeza dengan nama yang didaftarkan untuk pengembalian?
languages.cn: 如果存款名称与注册名称不同，我该怎么办以获得退款？

detailed.en: To process a refund when the deposit name differs from the registered name, please provide the account number and the name of the account holder. In this case, the account number is 08059023876047, and the account holder's name is Cik Nur Syaida Athirah Binti Ismail. We will then proceed with the refund to the account owner.
detailed.ms: Untuk memproses pengembalian apabila nama deposit berbeza daripada nama yang didaftarkan, sila berikan nombor akaun dan nama pemilik akaun. Dalam kes ini, nombor akaun adalah 08059023876047, dan nama pemilik akaun adalah Cik Nur Syaida Athirah Binti Ismail. Kami akan meneruskan pengembalian kepada pemilik akaun.
detailed.cn: 当存款名称与注册名称不同时，要处理退款，请提供账户号码和账户持有人的姓名。在这种情况下，账户号码是08059023876047，账户持有人的姓名是Cik Nur Syaida Athirah Binti Ismail。然后我们将继续向账户持有人退款。

question.text: Why has my balance disappeared from my account?

languages.en: Why has my balance disappeared from my account?
languages.ms: Kenapa balance saya hilang dari akaun saya?
languages.cn: 为什么我的账户余额消失了？

detailed.en: If your balance has disappeared, there could be several reasons. It might be that transactions have not been fully processed or there could be a technical issue. I recommend checking your account again, and if the problem persists, please contact our customer support for further assistance. Don't worry, we are here to help!
detailed.ms: Jika balance anda hilang, mungkin ada beberapa sebab. Mungkin transaksi belum diproses sepenuhnya atau ada masalah teknikal. Saya sarankan untuk memeriksa semula akaun anda dan jika masalah berterusan, sila hubungi sokongan pelanggan kami untuk bantuan lanjut. Jangan risau, kami sedia membantu!
detailed.cn: 如果您的余额消失，可能有几个原因。可能是交易尚未完全处理，或者可能存在技术问题。我建议您再次检查您的账户，如果问题仍然存在，请联系客户支持以获得进一步的帮助。别担心，我们在这里帮助您！

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt and how should I proceed with the banking process in the app?

detailed.en: After successfully uploading the receipt, please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. For banking, please use the bank account provided in your app and check the account details before topping up. Avoid saving the bank account as a favorite.
detailed.ms: Selepas berjaya mengupload resit, sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan upload resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin akan melambatkan sistem. Untuk banking, sila gunakan akaun bank yang disediakan dalam aplikasi anda dan semak butiran akaun sebelum topup. Elakkan menyimpan akaun bank sebagai kegemaran.

question.text: How can I return the money that I mistakenly transferred to the wrong bank account?
variations: boleh kasih return balik ka duit tu?
macam mna la sya sudah tranfer pergi akaun yg slalu pakai itu hari
ya..saya bru tahu skrang..tp saya sudah ter tranfer pergi bank lama k@z itu..

languages.en: How can I return the money that I mistakenly transferred to the wrong bank account?
languages.ms: Boleh kasih return balik ka duit tu?

detailed.en: I'm sorry, but if you have mistakenly transferred to the wrong account, the money cannot be refunded. However, you can still use the amount that has been credited for playing. Make sure to top-up correctly next time. If you have any other questions, feel free to ask!
detailed.ms: Maaf, boss, tetapi jika anda telah tersalah transfer ke akaun yang salah, duit itu tidak boleh dipulangkan. Namun, anda masih boleh menggunakan jumlah yang telah dikreditkan untuk bermain. Pastikan untuk top-up dengan betul selepas ini. Jika ada pertanyaan lain, jangan ragu untuk bertanya, ya!

question.text: How can I combine three receipts into one?
variations: bosku tolong gabungkan 3resit ini

languages.en: How can I combine three receipts into one?
languages.ms: bosku tolong gabungkan 3resit ini

detailed.en: To combine the three receipts, please take a screenshot of our conversation and upload it in the top-up section of the app as a receipt. Make sure to enter the amount of RM 79.2 when uploading. After submitting, wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to process the top-up. If you have any questions, feel free to contact us via live chat!
detailed.ms: Untuk menggabungkan tiga resit, sila ambil tangkapan skrin perbualan kita dan muat naik di bahagian topup dalam aplikasi sebagai resit. Pastikan untuk mengisi nilai RM 79.2 semasa muat naik. Selepas menghantar, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem memproses topup. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang pertanyaan, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami melalui live chat!

question.text: Can I get the win list for today and check the amounts for my 4D wins?
variations: What is the win list for today?
Can you provide today's win list?
How do I check my 4D win amounts?

languages.en: Can I get the win list for today and check the amounts for my 4D wins?
languages.ms: Bolehkah saya mendapatkan senarai kemenangan untuk hari ini dan menyemak jumlah kemenangan 4D saya?

detailed.en: For your 4D wins today, the amounts will be credited automatically to your wallet. This process usually takes between 1 to 10 minutes. Please check the 'Reports' section for confirmation. If your winnings do not appear after that time, feel free to contact our live chat support for assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk kemenangan 4D anda hari ini, jumlahnya akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Proses ini biasanya mengambil masa antara 1 hingga 10 minit. Sila semak bahagian 'Laporan' untuk pengesahan. Jika kemenangan anda tidak muncul selepas waktu tersebut, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi sokongan live chat kami.

question.text: What should I do if my transfer hasn't been credited yet?
variations: What to do if the transfer is delayed?
How long does it take for the transfer to reflect?

languages.en: What should I do if my transfer hasn't been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pemindahan saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If your credit hasn't been reflected yet, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. Please check the transaction in the app first. If it has been more than 10 minutes and you still don't see the credit, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for further inspection. We will assist you as soon as possible! 😊🙏
detailed.ms: Jika kredit anda belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu ya. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan masih tiada kredit, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin! 😊🙏

question.text: Why can't I access my 918Kiss account to play?
variations: kenapa acc kiss tak boleh main

languages.en: Why can't I access my 918Kiss account to play?
languages.ms: kenapa acc kiss tak boleh main

detailed.en: If you are having trouble accessing 918Kiss, try the following steps: 1. Close and reopen the 918Kiss app. 2. Log out and log back into the Joker app, then re-enter your ID and password. 3. Try switching your internet connection (from WiFi to data or vice versa). 4. Check if the game is under maintenance – if so, wait until it is completed. 5. Try reinstalling the game using the correct links: Download 918Kiss: https://m-918kiss.com or http://b1.918kiss.com. If the problem persists, please respond to us in the live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda menghadapi masalah untuk membuka 918Kiss, cuba langkah-langkah ini: 1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi 918Kiss. 2. Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam aplikasi Joker, kemudian salin semula ID dan kata laluan. 3. Cuba tukar sambungan internet (WiFi ke data atau sebaliknya). 4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan – jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai. 5. Cuba pasang semula permainan menggunakan pautan yang betul: Muat Turun 918Kiss: https://m-918kiss.com atau http://b1.918kiss.com. Jika masalah masih berterusan, balas kepada kami dalam chat langsung untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if I have more questions?

languages.en: What should I do if I have more questions?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya mempunyai lebih banyak soalan?
languages.cn: 如果我还有更多问题，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If you have any more questions, feel free to ask! I hope your day is filled with good fortune and prosperity!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mempunyai lebih banyak soalan, jangan segan untuk bertanya! Semoga hari anda dipenuhi dengan nasib baik dan kemakmuran!
detailed.cn: 如果您还有更多问题，请随时询问！希望您的一天充满好运和繁荣！

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas berjaya memuat naik resit?
languages.cn: 成功上传收据后我该怎么办？

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!
detailed.cn: 收据已成功上传。请稍等片刻以便系统处理。请不要再次上传相同的收据，因为这可能会减慢系统速度。感谢您的耐心和合作！

question.text: Saya telah bank in RM50 tetapi masih tidak masuk ke dalam akaun. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
variations: Duit yang saya bank in RM50 belum masuk, kenapa?
Bagaimana untuk menyemak status deposit RM50 saya?

languages.en: I have deposited RM50 but it hasn't appeared in my account. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah bank in RM50 tetapi masih tidak masuk ke dalam akaun. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have deposited RM50 and it hasn't appeared, please check the receipt to ensure all details are correct. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds are still not visible, please submit the receipt via live chat for further assistance. We are here to help!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah bank in RM50 dan masih tidak masuk, sila semak semula resit dan pastikan semua maklumat betul. Jika sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan masih tiada, hantarkan resit melalui live chat supaya kami dapat bantu semak. Kami di sini untuk membantu!

question.text: What should I do if I have already deposited money into my account but it hasn't reflected yet?
variations: What if my deposit isn't showing up?
What to do if the money is deducted but not credited?

languages.en: What should I do if I have already deposited money into my account but it hasn't reflected yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya sudah mendepositkan wang ke dalam akaun saya tetapi ia belum dipaparkan?

detailed.en: If the money has been deducted from your bank account but the deposit hasn't been successful, there may be a technical issue or a mistake with the receipt/transaction. Try to deposit again or send the receipt via live chat for further verification. If there's anything else I can assist you with, just let me know! 😊
detailed.ms: Jika duit telah ditolak dari akaun bank tetapi deposit tak berjaya, mungkin ada masalah teknikal atau kesilapan dengan resit/transaksi. Cuba buat deposit semula atau hantar resit melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Jika ada apa-apa yang boleh saya bantu, beritahu saja! 😊

question.text: What are the steps I need to follow for banking and topping up in the app?

languages.en: What are the steps I need to follow for banking and topping up in the app?
languages.ms: Apakah langkah-langkah yang perlu saya ikuti untuk perbankan dan menambah nilai dalam aplikasi?
languages.cn: 我需要遵循哪些步骤才能在应用程序中进行银行业务和充值？

detailed.en: Please use the bank account provided in your app for banking. Make sure to check your bank account in the app before topping up. Do not save the bank account as a favorite. Also, ensure that you do not upload the same receipt again, as it may slow down the system.
detailed.ms: Sila gunakan akaun bank yang disediakan dalam aplikasi anda untuk perbankan. Pastikan anda menyemak akaun bank anda dalam aplikasi sebelum menambah nilai. Jangan simpan akaun bank sebagai kegemaran. Juga, pastikan anda tidak memuat naik resit yang sama lagi, kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem.
detailed.cn: 请使用您应用程序中提供的银行账户进行银行业务。在充值之前，请确保检查您在应用程序中的银行账户。不要将银行账户保存为收藏。此外，请确保您不要再次上传相同的收据，因为这可能会减慢系统速度。

question.text: What should I do if I accidentally shared credit with the wrong ID?
variations: What can I do if I sent credit to the wrong account?
How can I recover credit sent to the wrong ID?

languages.en: What should I do if I accidentally shared credit with the wrong ID?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya secara tidak sengaja berkongsi kredit dengan ID yang salah?

detailed.en: If you have shared credit with the wrong ID, please provide the incorrect JOKER ID and the amount of credit involved. We will try to contact the owner of that ID and request them to return the credit in the same way (Share Credit). However, there is no guarantee that the credit can be returned, as it depends on the owner of the ID who received it. In the future, make sure the ID entered is correct before pressing send.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah berkongsi kredit dengan ID yang salah, sila berikan JOKER ID yang anda kongsi secara salah dan jumlah kredit yang terlibat. Kami akan cuba menghubungi pemilik ID tersebut dan meminta mereka untuk mengembalikan kredit dengan cara yang sama (Kongsi Kredit). Namun, tiada jaminan kredit dapat dikembalikan, ia bergantung kepada pemilik ID yang menerimanya. Lain kali, pastikan ID yang dimasukkan adalah betul sebelum menekan hantar.

question.text: What should I do if I cannot send the receipt for my transaction?
variations: How can I send my receipt?
I'm having trouble uploading my receipt, what should I do?

languages.en: What should I do if I cannot send the receipt for my transaction?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat menghantar resit untuk transaksi saya?

detailed.en: If you cannot send the receipt, you can try the following steps: 1. Restart your phone or close and reopen the app. 2. Try switching your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa). 3. Ensure your internet connection is stable before trying again. If the problem persists, you can send the receipt directly to live chat for further assistance. We will help process it for you!
detailed.ms: Jika anda tidak dapat menghantar resit, mungkin anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah ini: 1. Mulakan semula telefon anda atau tutup dan buka semula aplikasi. 2. Cuba tukar rangkaian internet (WiFi ke data mudah alih atau sebaliknya). 3. Pastikan sambungan internet anda stabil sebelum mencuba lagi. Jika masalah masih berterusan, anda boleh hantarkan resit terus ke live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu prosesnya untuk anda!

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas berjaya memuat naik resit?
languages.cn: 成功上传收据后我该怎么办？

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!
detailed.cn: 收据已成功上传。请稍等片刻以便系统处理。请不要再次上传相同的收据，因为这可能会减慢系统速度。感谢您的耐心和合作！

question.text: What should I do if my deposit is taking too long to process?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit is taking too long to process?

detailed.en: If your deposit is taking too long, it usually takes between 5 to 30 minutes. If you feel like you are waiting too long, please let me know, and I will check it for you!

question.text: What should I do to top up my account using the banking app?

languages.en: What should I do to top up my account using the banking app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan untuk menambah nilai akaun saya menggunakan aplikasi perbankan?
languages.cn: 我该如何使用银行应用程序为我的账户充值？

detailed.en: Please use the bank account provided in your app for banking. Make sure to check the bank account in your app before topping up. Do not save the bank account as a favorite.
detailed.ms: Sila gunakan akaun bank yang disediakan dalam aplikasi anda untuk perbankan. Pastikan anda menyemak akaun bank dalam aplikasi anda sebelum menambah nilai. Jangan simpan akaun bank sebagai kegemaran.
detailed.cn: 请使用您应用中提供的银行账户进行银行业务。在充值之前，请确保检查您应用中的银行账户。请勿将银行账户保存为收藏。

question.text: Is my deposit already credited to my wallet?
variations: sudah ka deposit?
Is my deposit in my wallet yet?

languages.en: Is my deposit already credited to my wallet?
languages.ms: sudah ka deposit?

detailed.en: If your deposit has been banked in but not credited to your wallet, please check your wallet to confirm. If it is still not there, you can contact our live chat support with the transaction details for further assistance. If you topped up from Touch 'n Go/BANK, please let me know if you used ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX) so I can assist you further. If you used ATM/Transfer (DuitNow), ensure the receipt has been uploaded to the top-up page in the app and wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If you used Fast Payment (FPX), it usually enters within 1-10 minutes; if it has not entered after 10 minutes, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification. If you still have issues, feel free to reach out to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika deposit anda sudah bank in tetapi belum dikredit ke wallet, sila semak wallet anda untuk memastikan. Jika masih tiada, anda boleh hubungi sokongan live chat kami dengan butiran transaksi untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika anda topup dari Touch 'n Go/BANK, boleh saya tahu anda guna ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX)? Supaya saya boleh bantu semak untuk anda. Jika guna ATM/Transfer (DuitNow), pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan. Jika guna Fast Payment (FPX), biasanya masuk dalam 1-10 minit; kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan. Kalau masih ada masalah, boleh roger kami di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut ya.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?
languages.cn: 上传收据后我该怎么办？

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!
detailed.cn: 收据已成功上传。请稍等片刻以便系统处理。请不要再次上传相同的收据，因为这可能会减慢系统速度。感谢您的耐心和合作！

question.text: What should I do if I haven't received any notifications about my 4D winnings?
variations: Why is there a delay in receiving notifications for my 4D winnings?
What can I do if I usually receive notifications quickly but haven't this time?

languages.en: What should I do if I haven't received any notifications about my 4D winnings?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya belum menerima sebarang pemberitahuan tentang kemenangan 4D saya?

detailed.en: If you haven't received any notifications about your 4D winnings, please be patient as the system is processing. The winnings will automatically be credited to your wallet. You can check the app from time to time for updates. If the issue persists, try logging out and logging back in. If you still face problems, feel free to reach out for assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda belum menerima sebarang pemberitahuan tentang kemenangan 4D anda, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses. Duit kemenangan akan dimasukkan secara automatik ke dalam wallet anda. Anda boleh menyemak aplikasi dari semasa ke semasa untuk kemas kini. Jika masalah berterusan, cuba log keluar dan log masuk semula. Jika anda masih menghadapi masalah, sila hubungi untuk bantuan.

question.text: How can I withdraw money from my account?
variations: mau withdraw bos

languages.en: How can I withdraw money from my account?
languages.ms: Mau withdraw bos

detailed.en:
To withdraw money, follow these steps in the app:

1️⃣ Click the 'Wallet' icon (at the bottom center of the screen).
2️⃣ Select 'Withdraw'.
3️⃣ Ensure the selected bank account has a 'Primary' tag.
4️⃣ Enter the amount you wish to withdraw (Min RM10).
5️⃣ Click 'Submit' to send the withdrawal request.
6️⃣ Wait 5-30 minutes for the process to complete.

📌 Important:
✅ The name of the bank account owner must match the name registered in the app.
✅ If the bank account has not been added or you want to change it, update it first before submitting.

If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk melakukan pengeluaran, ikut langkah-langkah ini dalam aplikasi:

1️⃣ Klik ikon 'Wallet' (di tengah bawah skrin).
2️⃣ Pilih 'Withdraw'.
3️⃣ Pastikan akaun bank yang dipilih mempunyai tanda 'Primary'.
4️⃣ Masukkan jumlah yang ingin dikeluarkan (Min RM10).
5️⃣ Klik 'Submit' untuk menghantar permohonan pengeluaran.
6️⃣ Tunggu 5-30 minit untuk proses selesai.

📌 Penting:
✅ Nama pemilik akaun bank mesti sepadan dengan nama yang didaftarkan dalam aplikasi.
✅ Jika akaun bank belum ditambah atau anda ingin menukarnya, kemas kini terlebih dahulu sebelum menghantar.

Jika ada sebarang masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya, boss! 😊🙏

question.text: How can I transfer money using Touch 'n Go eWallet and what should I do if I made a mistake in the transfer?
variations: Can you guide me on transferring money with TNG eWallet?

languages.en: How can I transfer money using Touch 'n Go eWallet and what should I do if I made a mistake in the transfer?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh memindahkan wang menggunakan eWallet Touch 'n Go dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya membuat kesilapan dalam pemindahan?

detailed.en: To transfer using Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, follow these steps: 1. Open TNG eWallet and go to the 'Transfer' section. 2. Select DuitNow Transfer. 3. Enter our company's bank account number (refer to the top-up page). 4. Enter the correct amount (Min RM10 for ATM/Transfer, Min RM50 for Fast Payment). 5. Confirm the transaction and take a screenshot of the complete receipt. 6. Upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat. 7. Wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. Important: You must use DuitNow Transfer (not regular eWallet transfer). The account owner's name must match the name in the app to avoid rejection. If you have any issues, reply to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk memindahkan menggunakan eWallet Touch 'n Go (TNG), ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka TNG eWallet dan pergi ke bahagian 'Transfer'. 2. Pilih DuitNow Transfer. 3. Masukkan nombor akaun bank syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up). 4. Masukkan jumlah yang betul (Min RM10 untuk ATM/Transfer, Min RM50 untuk Fast Payment). 5. question.text: How can I ensure my bank transfer is successful if the ATM slip does not print?

detailed.en: If you have transferred using the ATM but the slip did not come out, please take a screenshot or proof of the transaction and upload it in the top-up section of the app. The process usually takes 3-10 minutes; if it takes longer than that, please contact live chat with the full screenshot. question.text: How can I top up my e-wallet using Touch 'n Go?

languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top-up e-wallet saya menggunakan Touch 'n Go?
languages.cn: 我如何使用Touch 'n Go充值我的电子钱包？

detailed.en:
To top-up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, follow these steps:

1️⃣ Open the TNG eWallet app.
2️⃣ Select 'DuitNow Transfer' for manual method or 'Fast Payment (FPX)' for quicker transactions.
3️⃣ Enter the company's bank account number (refer to the top-up page in the app).
4️⃣ Enter the top-up amount (min RM10 for DuitNow, min RM50 for FPX).
5️⃣ Confirm the transaction and take a screenshot of the receipt.
6️⃣ If using DuitNow, upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app.
7️⃣ Wait 3-10 minutes for transaction confirmation.

📌 Important:
✅ Ensure the account owner's name matches the name in the app to avoid rejection.

If you encounter any issues, please reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top-up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, ikut langkah-langkah ini:

1️⃣ Buka aplikasi TNG eWallet.
2️⃣ Pilih 'DuitNow Transfer' jika anda ingin menggunakan kaedah manual, atau pilih 'Fast Payment (FPX)' untuk transaksi yang lebih cepat.
3️⃣ Masukkan nombor akaun bank syarikat (rujuk pada halaman top-up dalam aplikasi).
4️⃣ Masukkan jumlah top-up (min RM10 untuk DuitNow, min RM50 untuk FPX).
5️⃣ Sahkan transaksi dan ambil tangkapan skrin resit.
6️⃣ Jika menggunakan DuitNow, muat naik resit ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi.
7️⃣ Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan transaksi.

📌 Penting:
✅ Pastikan nama pemilik akaun sepadan dengan nama dalam aplikasi untuk mengelakkan penolakan.

Jika ada sebarang masalah, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya!
detailed.cn:
要使用Touch 'n Go (TNG)电子钱包充值，请按照以下步骤操作：

1️⃣ 打开TNG电子钱包应用程序。
2️⃣ 选择“DuitNow转账”以手动方式，或选择“快速支付（FPX）”以更快的交易。
3️⃣ 输入公司的银行账户号码（请参阅应用程序中的充值页面）。
4️⃣ 输入充值金额（DuitNow最低RM10，FPX最低RM50）。
5️⃣ 确认交易并截屏收据。
6️⃣ 如果使用DuitNow，请将收据上传到应用程序中的充值页面。
7️⃣ 等待3-10分钟以确认交易。

📌 重要：
✅ 确保账户持有者的姓名与应用程序中的姓名匹配，以避免拒绝。

如果您遇到任何问题，请在实时聊天中回复我们！

detailed.en:
To withdraw money to your bank account, follow these steps in the app:

1️⃣ Click the 'Wallet' icon (at the bottom center of the screen).
2️⃣ Select 'Withdraw'.
3️⃣ Ensure the selected bank account has a 'Primary' tag.
4️⃣ Enter the amount you wish to withdraw (Min RM10).
5️⃣ Click 'Submit' to send the withdrawal request.
6️⃣ Wait 5-30 minutes for the process to complete.

📌 Important:
✅ The name of the bank account holder must match the name registered in the app.
✅ If the bank account has not been added or you want to change it, update it first before submitting.

If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat!

languages.en: When will my winnings from J2 be credited to my account?
languages.ms: Bila duit kemenangan J2 akan dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: The winnings from J2/J3 will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. If it has been more than 30 minutes and the amount is still not credited, please contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.

question.text: What are the best practices for managing personal finances effectively?
variations: How can I manage my finances better?
What tips do you have for personal finance management?
What strategies should I use for effective financial management?

languages.en: What are the best practices for managing personal finances effectively?

detailed.en: To manage personal finances effectively, consider the following best practices: 1. Create a budget to track your income and expenses. 2. Set financial goals, both short-term and long-term. 3. Build an emergency fund to cover unexpected expenses. 4. Pay off high-interest debts as a priority. 5. Invest in retirement accounts to secure your future. 6. Regularly review and adjust your financial plan as needed.

question.text: What should I do if my login is taking a long time to load in the Joker App?

languages.en: What should I do if my login is taking a long time to load in the Joker App?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika login saya mengambil masa yang lama untuk dimuatkan dalam aplikasi Joker?

detailed.en: To resolve the slow login issue in the Joker App, you can try the following steps: 1. Close and reopen the game app. 2. Logout and log back into the Joker App, then re-enter your ID and Password. 3. Change your internet connection (try WiFi or mobile data). 4. Check if the game is under maintenance – if it is, wait until it is completed. 5. If you still cannot log in, try using a VPN. You can download a VPN for Malaysia from the link provided. After installing the VPN, connect to Malaysia and then try logging in again. If the problem persists, send a screenshot to live chat for immediate assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk menyelesaikan masalah login yang lambat dalam aplikasi Joker, anda boleh mencuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi permainan. 2. Logout dan log masuk semula ke aplikasi Joker, kemudian masukkan semula ID dan Kata Laluan anda. 3. Tukar sambungan internet anda (cuba WiFi atau data mudah alih). 4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan - jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai. 5. Jika anda masih tidak dapat log masuk, cuba gunakan VPN. Anda boleh memuat turun VPN untuk Malaysia dari pautan yang disediakan. Selepas memasang VPN, sambungkan ke Malaysia dan cuba log masuk semula. Jika masalah berterusan, hantarkan tangkapan skrin ke live chat untuk bantuan segera.

question.text: What are the options for withdrawing winnings of 100k?
variations: What can I do if I win 100k?
How can I withdraw my winnings of 100k?

languages.en: What are the options for withdrawing winnings of 100k?
languages.ms: Apakah pilihan untuk mengeluarkan kemenangan sebanyak 100k?
languages.cn: 如果我赢得100k，我可以怎么提取我的奖金？

detailed.en:
If you win with the number 100k, you have several options for withdrawal:

1. **Direct Transfer**: You can withdraw the full amount directly (the process usually takes 5-30 minutes).
2. **Partial Withdrawal**: You can split the withdrawal into smaller amounts for more flexibility.
3. **Using Company Account**: For winnings above 100k, you can choose to use a company account to 'wash' the funds, which simplifies the process for large amounts.

I hope this information helps!
detailed.ms:
Jika anda menang dengan nombor 100k, anda mempunyai beberapa pilihan untuk pengeluaran:

1. **Pemindahan Langsung**: Anda boleh mengeluarkan jumlah penuh secara langsung (proses biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit).
2. **Pengeluaran Sebahagian**: Anda boleh membahagikan pengeluaran kepada jumlah yang lebih kecil untuk lebih fleksibiliti.
3. **Menggunakan Akaun Syarikat**: Untuk kemenangan di atas 100k, anda boleh memilih untuk menggunakan akaun syarikat untuk 'mencuci' dana, yang memudahkan proses untuk jumlah besar.

Semoga maklumat ini membantu!
detailed.cn:
如果您赢得100k，您有几种提款选项：

1. **直接转账**：您可以直接提取全额（该过程通常需要5-30分钟）。
2. **部分提款**：您可以将提款分成较小的金额以获得更多灵活性。
3. **使用公司账户**：对于超过100k的奖金，您可以选择使用公司账户来“洗”资金，这简化了大额提款的过程。

希望这些信息对您有所帮助！

detailed.en: If your fast payment (FPX) is delayed, please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the funds should appear within 1-10 minutes. detailed.en: If you forget to enter your JOKER ID during the transfer, don't worry! Make sure your transaction receipt is complete and clear. Upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app as usual. Wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to verify the transaction. For future transfers, ensure you write the JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' field so the system can verify it faster. If you have any issues or need assistance, feel free to contact us via live chat.

Untuk masa akan datang, pastikan anda menulis ID JOKER dalam ruangan 'Recipient Reference' supaya sistem dapat mengesahkan lebih cepat. question.text: Saya telah menghantar ID yang salah, adakah mungkin untuk mendapatkan refund?

languages.ms: Saya telah menghantar ID yang salah, adakah mungkin untuk mendapatkan refund?

detailed.en: If you have sent the wrong ID, unfortunately, the system cannot process a refund automatically. Please provide the incorrect JOKER ID and the amount of credits involved. We will try to contact the owner of that ID and request them to return the credits in the same way (Credit Share). However, there is no guarantee that the credits can be returned, as it depends on the owner of the ID who received it. In the future, please ensure that the ID entered is correct before pressing the send button.
detailed.ms: Jika anda tersalah hantar ID, maaf ya, sistem tidak dapat memproses refund secara automatik. Sila berikan JOKER ID yang anda hantar secara salah dan jumlah kredit yang terlibat. Kami akan cuba menghubungi pemilik ID tersebut dan meminta mereka untuk mengembalikan kredit dengan cara yang sama (Credit Share). Namun, tiada jaminan kredit dapat dikembalikan, ia bergantung kepada pemilik ID yang menerimanya. Lain kali, pastikan ID yang dimasukkan adalah betul sebelum menekan butang hantar ya!

question.text: What should I do if the Mega888 link is not working or if the login is taking too long?
variations: Mega888 link not working
Login loading too long

languages.en: What should I do if the Mega888 link is not working or if the login is taking too long?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pautan Mega888 tidak berfungsi atau jika login mengambil masa terlalu lama?
languages.cn: 如果Mega888链接无法使用或登录时间过长，我该怎么办？

detailed.en: If the Mega888 link is not clickable, you can copy the link and paste it into your web browser's address bar, then press 'Enter' to start the download. You can also try using a different browser or check your browser settings. If you are experiencing long loading times when logging in, you can try the following steps: Close and reopen the game app, log out and log back into the Joker App, then re-enter your ID and Password. Change your internet connection (try WiFi or mobile data). Check if the game is under maintenance – if it is, wait until it is completed. You can also use a VPN if you still cannot access it. Download a VPN for Malaysia, install it, open the app, connect to Malaysia, and then try logging in again. If you still have issues, please send a screenshot to live chat for immediate assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika pautan Mega888 tidak boleh diklik, anda boleh salin pautan tersebut dan tampal ke dalam bar alamat pelayar web anda, kemudian tekan 'Enter' untuk memulakan muat turun. Anda juga boleh cuba menggunakan pelayar yang berbeza atau semak tetapan pelayar anda. Jika anda mengalami masa muat yang lama semasa log masuk, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: Tutup & buka semula aplikasi permainan, log keluar dan log masuk semula ke aplikasi Joker, kemudian masukkan semula ID & Kata Laluan anda. Tukar rangkaian internet (cuba WiFi atau data mudah alih). Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan - jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai. Anda juga boleh menggunakan VPN jika masih tidak dapat mengaksesnya. Muat turun VPN untuk Malaysia, pasang, buka aplikasi, sambung ke Malaysia, dan kemudian cuba log masuk semula. Jika anda masih mempunyai masalah, sila hantar tangkapan skrin ke sembang langsung untuk bantuan segera.
detailed.cn: 如果Mega888链接无法点击，您可以复制链接并将其粘贴到您的网络浏览器地址栏中，然后按“Enter”开始下载。您还可以尝试使用不同的浏览器或检查浏览器设置。如果您在登录时遇到长时间加载的问题，可以尝试以下步骤：关闭并重新打开游戏应用程序，注销并重新登录Joker应用程序，然后重新输入您的ID和密码。更改您的互联网连接（尝试WiFi或移动数据）。检查游戏是否正在维护 - 如果是，请等待完成。如果您仍然无法访问，可以使用VPN。下载马来西亚的VPN，安装它，打开应用程序，连接到马来西亚，然后尝试再次登录。如果您仍然有问题，请将屏幕截图发送到在线聊天以获得即时帮助。

detailed.en: If the RM70 transaction was mistakenly transferred to your own bank account, unfortunately, the money cannot be refunded. However, you can still use the credited amount to play. Make sure to top-up correctly by uploading the bank-in receipt through (WALLET → TOPUP). After sending, wait 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. If the credit does not arrive within 10 minutes, please contact customer support for further assistance.

detailed.cn: 如果70令吉的交易错误地转入您自己的银行账户，不幸的是，钱无法退还。但是，您仍然可以使用已入账的金额进行游戏。确保通过(WALLET → TOPUP)正确充值并上传银行存款收据。发送后，请等待3-10分钟以便系统处理交易。如果在10分钟内未收到入账，请联系客户支持以获取进一步的帮助。

detailed.en: The minimum withdrawal amount is RM30. You need to achieve a 30% turnover from your deposit before you can withdraw. For example, if you top up RM100, you need to win enough to reach a turnover of RM130 (which is RM100 + 30%). If your balance is less than RM30, you need to accumulate more before you can withdraw. If you have any other questions, feel free to contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Jumlah minimum untuk pengeluaran adalah RM30. Anda perlu mencapai 30% turnover daripada deposit sebelum boleh mengeluarkan. Sebagai contoh, jika anda topup RM100, anda perlu menang untuk mencapai turnover RM130 (iaitu RM100 + 30%). Jika baki anda kurang daripada RM30, anda perlu mengumpul lagi sebelum boleh mengeluarkan. question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk top up menggunakan TNG eWallet dengan Fast Payment (FPX)?
variations: Apa langkah-langkah untuk top up TNG eWallet?
Bolehkah anda beritahu cara top up menggunakan FPX?

languages.ms: Bagaimana cara untuk top up menggunakan TNG eWallet dengan Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.ms:
Untuk top up guna Fast Payment (FPX) dengan TNG eWallet, ikut langkah-langkah ini:

1️⃣ Buka aplikasi TNG eWallet dan pergi ke halaman top-up.
2️⃣ Pilih Fast Payment (FPX) dan pilih TNG eWallet.
3️⃣ Masukkan jumlah top-up yang diingini (min RM50).
4️⃣ Sahkan transaksi dalam aplikasi TNG eWallet.
5️⃣ Tunggu 1-3 minit untuk dana dikreditkan secara automatik.

📌 Penting:
✅ Pastikan anda memilih TNG eWallet dalam bahagian pembayaran.
✅ Jika tiada kredit selepas 3 minit, hantar resit transaksi FPX ke live chat untuk semakan.

detailed.en: To ensure your transfer is processed correctly, please upload the complete receipt to the top-up page in the app, not in the chat. The receipt must include: the date and time of the transaction, the amount transferred, the recipient's details (our company account), and the successful transaction status. After uploading, wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to verify. If there are any issues, reply to us in the chat for further checks.
detailed.ms: Untuk memastikan pemindahan anda diproses dengan betul, sila muat naik resit lengkap ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan di dalam chat. Resit tersebut mesti termasuk: tarikh dan masa transaksi, jumlah yang dipindahkan, butiran penerima (akaun syarikat kami), dan status transaksi yang berjaya. Selepas memuat naik, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika ada masalah, balas kepada kami dalam chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up using TNG has not been credited to my account?
variations: What to do if TNG top-up is not showing?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up using TNG has not been credited to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika tambah nilai menggunakan TNG belum masuk ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: If your top-up using TNG has not been credited, it usually takes 1-3 minutes. If it has been more than 3 minutes and it still hasn't appeared, please check the transaction in the app first. If it is still not there, send your FPX transaction receipt to live chat for further verification. We will assist in processing it as quickly as possible! If you upload the same receipt twice, the system may reject the transaction and it will need to be processed again, which will take longer. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, only then send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate checking. Please be patient, the system will process it as quickly as possible!

Jika sudah lebih dari 3 minit dan masih belum muncul, sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika masih tiada, hantarkan resit transaksi FPX anda ke live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu proses secepat mungkin! Jika anda upload resit yang sama dua kali, sistem mungkin akan reject transaksi dan perlu proses semula, jadi lebih lambat. question.text: How can I get a full receipt from the Public Bank app?

languages.en: How can I get a full receipt from the Public Bank app?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh mendapatkan resit penuh dari aplikasi Public Bank?

detailed.en: To get a full receipt from the Public Bank app (PBB), please follow these steps: 1. Open the PBB app. 2. Tap on the Transaction History section. 3. Select PBe History. 4. Tap on the transaction you made (e.g., -RM200.00). 5. Tap Share to WhatsApp or take a screenshot using another phone. 6. Upload that image to the Topup section in the JOKER app. If you are still unsure, you can send me the image or contact me, and I will help you check.
detailed.ms: Untuk mendapatkan resit penuh dari aplikasi Public Bank (PBB), sila ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka aplikasi PBB. 2. Tekan bahagian Sejarah Transaksi. 3. Pilih Sejarah PBe. 4. Tekan transaksi yang anda buat (contoh: -RM200.00). 5. Tekan Kongsi ke WhatsApp atau ambil tangkapan skrin menggunakan telefon lain. 6. Muat naik gambar itu ke bahagian Topup dalam aplikasi JOKER. Jika anda masih tidak pasti, anda boleh menghantar gambar itu kepada saya atau hubungi saya, dan saya akan membantu anda menyemak.

question.text: Can I use Touch 'n Go (TNG) for top-up transactions?
variations: kalau in pakai tng png boleh tak

languages.en: Can I use Touch 'n Go (TNG) for top-up transactions?
languages.ms: Kalau in pakai Touch 'n Go (TNG) untuk top-up, boleh tak?

detailed.en:
To use Touch 'n Go (TNG) for top-up, ensure you follow the correct steps. If you encounter issues, try the following methods:

1. Ensure you are using the correct method:
   - If using Fast Payment (FPX):
     - Select TNG eWallet in the payment section.
     - Wait 1-3 minutes for the system to automatically confirm the transaction.
     - If it does not appear after 3 minutes, send the FPX transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
   - If using DuitNow Transfer via TNG:
     - Make sure to select DuitNow to the bank account number, not a regular eWallet transfer.
     - Manually upload the transaction receipt to the top-up page in the app.
     - Wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm.

2. If you still have issues, try:
   - Switching your internet connection (WiFi/Data).
   - Checking if TNG is undergoing maintenance.
   - Trying other methods like ATM/Transfer.

If you still cannot succeed, reply to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms:
Untuk menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) untuk top-up, pastikan anda mengikuti langkah-langkah yang betul. Jika ada masalah, boleh cuba cara-cara berikut:

1. Pastikan anda menggunakan kaedah yang betul:
   - Jika menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX):
     - Pilih TNG eWallet dalam bahagian pembayaran.
     - Tunggu 1-3 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi secara automatik.
     - Jika tidak masuk selepas 3 minit, hantar resit transaksi FPX ke live chat untuk semakan.
   - Jika menggunakan DuitNow Transfer melalui TNG:
     - Pastikan anda memilih DuitNow ke nombor akaun bank, bukan pemindahan eWallet biasa.
     - Muat naik resit transaksi secara manual ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi.
     - Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan.

2. Jika masih ada masalah, cuba:
   - Tukar rangkaian internet (WiFi/Data).
   - Semak jika TNG sedang dalam penyelenggaraan.
   - Cuba kaedah lain seperti ATM/Pindahan.

Jika masih tidak berjaya, balas kepada kami di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk melakukan transfer dari TNG eWallet ke akaun bank Maybank dan apa yang perlu ditulis?

languages.en: How to transfer from TNG eWallet to Maybank account and what should be written?
languages.ms: Bagaimana cara untuk melakukan transfer dari TNG eWallet ke akaun bank Maybank dan apa yang perlu ditulis?

detailed.en: To transfer from TNG eWallet to a Maybank account, follow these steps: 1. Select DuitNow Transfer in the TNG eWallet app. 2. Enter the Maybank account number you wish to transfer to. 3. Input the amount you want to transfer. 4. Confirm the transaction and take a screenshot of the receipt as proof. Example message: 'Transfer RM50 from TNG eWallet to Maybank account 1234567890.' Ensure the account holder's name matches the name in the app to avoid issues.
detailed.ms: Untuk memindahkan dari TNG eWallet ke akaun Maybank, ikuti langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Pilih DuitNow Transfer dalam aplikasi TNG eWallet. 2. Masukkan nombor akaun Maybank yang ingin anda transfer. 3. Masukkan jumlah yang ingin dipindahkan. 4. Sahkan transaksi dan ambil tangkapan skrin resit sebagai bukti. Contoh pesanan: 'Transfer RM50 dari TNG eWallet ke akaun Maybank 1234567890.' Pastikan nama pemilik akaun Maybank sepadan dengan nama dalam aplikasi untuk mengelakkan sebarang masalah.
